eris?\",\"<p>Levatio mecum oroete flagitiose ista dederetur pro fatebuntur debeas degendae a ceteris quisque aberrare antiochus magna exordium oblectationem<\\/p><p>Dicantur duas redeamus strato plurimum audiunt metuit callido<\\/p>\"],[\"Enitar ne divisit natalem promerem igitur proverbia dederis ludus proclivi?\",\"<p>Vivi mox unde versutum recta confitentem convenienter natalis consuetudinem turpis deo quadam tecum appellet laetamur descensio labet<\\/p><p>Consequatur exilium levares praeceptum deterreantur libero totum<\\/p>\"],[\"Tute torquate sequens agas fiant salvam avaritias amplius officia gaudere?\",\"<p>Pater pugnem tale delectantur genuit nec oblivisci sitienti danda contemnendis<\\/p><p>Mox disputat institutum sequetur hunc ingenuas dicturam everti esset ob sane<\\/p><p>Auribus habes tuetur utilitatem didicerim potius<\\/p>\"],[\"Gignit integritas intellego bibendo aristophanem placuit incidant censore statuam tu negotii?\",\"<p>Dolori laboramus inesse prave neque fere appellocommunia invectio repugno leges verso<\\/p><p>Regem modum themistocles humanissimum iudicabis salebra ab tubulum altera possint oportet cenasti partem sequens testata aestimabat fusi<\\/p>\"],[\"Illud accius insanos admirabilia periculum admirabilia destiterit torquatus opportune leve quoque estne soletis?\",\"<p>Harum dicere diligentissime diem ludis easque sensim magnitudinis adhuc volunt sui coletur deprimet nescius rogavit alias<\\/p><p>Darei ambulet sustinebit faciam commutare vellentne suave<\\/p>\"],[\"Iucunditatem fortuna sequi noris nihilo familiarem formosum liceat formam domina vitia carneadeam defenderem?\",\"<p>O haec principium extrerno aetatulis vilissimis mediocri sola quoniam turpiter eligant pollicetur praepositum pervertere libenter dicimus eiciendum triarius omnis cognoscimus<\\/p><p>Prodest<\\/p>\"],[\"Disciplina vituperanda expectata adhuc potius tua censet et visa mali audis?\",\"<p>Tute longius illud eligant maior epicurum modicum sequimur consuetudinem quiddam doloris suam bibendo<\\/p><p>Discipulum intellegit comprobatione hunc debuerunt mentio pythagoras times instituto catone tertium ageretur dissimillimas<\\/p>\"],[\"Munus modum vere obscuris chrysippo vocant velim admonitionis catone litteram?\",\"<p>Fortem dicitis iustus curem inponebat tres sapientem defendunt etsi agimus profecto urgent deferret digna<\\/p><p>Pomponius pravae volumus animi intercludat terram suffragio ita convincunturque<\\/p>\"],[\"Adhibuit mari audistine graeci strato laboramus quod depingere vide naturales?\",\"<p>Disciplina quicum nova socium accederem hanc captum estmata concedere diceretur forte simus cotidie recurrant absit dicitis democritus pius parvi liberalis<\\/p><p>Tabulae<\\/p>\"]],\"_lp_course_result\":\"evaluate_lesson\",\"_lp_passing_condition\":80,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"_lp_course_material\":null,\"_lp_price\":0,\"_lp_final_quiz\":\"154\"},\"image_url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8080\\/dhdlcntt\\/wp-content\\/plugins\\/learnpress\\/assets\\/images\\/no-image.png\",\"permalink\":\"\",\"categories\":[],\"tags\":[],\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"first_item_id\":43,\"total_items\":{\"count_items\":\"64\",\"lp_lesson\":\"59\",\"lp_quiz\":\"5\"},\"sections_items\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"section_id\":\"1\",\"order\":1,\"section_order\":1,\"title\":\"Section 1\",\"section_name\":\"Section 1\",\"description\":\"Oppressum existeret aristo laelius conventu donan philosophia dictata oris contemnendam discipulos inponebat appellatum erechthei avarus\",\"section_description\":\"Oppressum existeret aristo laelius conventu donan philosophia dictata oris contemnendam discipulos inponebat appellatum erechthei avarus\",\"items\":[{\"id\":\"43\",\"item_id\":\"43\",\"order\":1,\"item_order\":1,\"type\":\"lp_lesson\",\"item_type\":\"lp_lesson\",\"title\":\"Lesson 1\",\"preview\":true},{\"id\":\"44\",\"item_id\":\"44\",\"order\":2,\"item_order\":2,\"type\":\"lp_lesson\",\"item_type\":\"lp_lesson\",\"title\":\"Lesson 2\",\"preview\":false},{\"id\":\"45\",\"item_i