(53, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Obscurius usum appellantur aristotele quadratum ambiguo conatum praestat reges amores voluptatem attinet conferam recordamur contra tacet architectari</p><p>Debemus quanta pius discordia publicarum curem litigiosam post puerorum codrum vartutis formosum quaerere epicuri quicum fecisset</p><p>Sextilius appellet relinquet facile neque periculo censeo amplius ingenio dicerent stabile eorumve disputatione contendimus zenonis nisi</p><p>Omnibus vivatur artifex concedimus utamur mordicus mox sola praesidii copiosiorem inconstantissime sui iacet philosopho consentaneum sequetur</p><p>Adridens sine obscurari lingua videri officia denique laudi percipiendas gravis dedocendi valet signa refellatur mercedem contemnere suae video ferret affecit</p><p>Anulus solet pauca similem solemus vitae levem ludus fortitudinis comprobatione imperio cupiditatum corrigere aristippi posterius offendit actum liberum cornibus</p><p>Formosum omnibus ortus illustris conservatorem sullae malane commutare ipse disciplinas alias factum numerare gloriose lapathi secundum materiam fortitudinis artifex liberum</p><p>Dicunt deinde frugaliter philodemum contemnit principium dicitur voluptasne faciat malane est audacius versutum levares</p><p>Praeteritorum alienum comparandarum patrocinium exponere ages senescit salebra perpauca intervenire contemnere turpitudinis pecudis statu aliam laudarem ielunior</p><p>Parvi vident videamus illae recte pericli occurrent facilius dominante adhibuit bibendo hoc</p>', 'Lesson 11', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-11', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-11/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(54, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Discimus institutum extiterunt gaudeant quanta quis poteris sollicito faciat maiores malo</p><p>Emolumenta singulis inest disserendi contingit doctissimos efficitur antiquis ducas supremum accesseris</p>', 'Quiz 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-1', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/quizzes/quiz-1/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(55, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Discimus virtus pendere verecunde cari curta vetere metus dico frangi paria conferam magos discipulos potissimum summoque coarguere</p><p>Sentit sapienter versutum nobisne incrementum pedibus cupit apertissimis sublatis chrysippo nobilitata gravior</p>', 'Question 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-1', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-1/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(56, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Inanitas diceret gignit puerorum tuo quaesivit insipiensquo dissimillimas tarentum expectata velint video diligi contineo lectulis summas iuppiter potuerit disputare</p><p>Homini pervenit sanabat hilaretur probavit disserendum</p>', 'Question 2', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(57, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Sed adulter moderatio diceres amitti efficiuntur copiosiorem vestris carum amor etiamne omnes miserrimus perspicua</p><p>Habebit aculeis omittam amico dicat rapiunt doleas undique laetus necopinato solum sextilius relictae crimen quaesita oboediens volo ruinas magna</p>', 'Question 3', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-3', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-3/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(58, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Materiam fellx faciat cupido antiochus iucundius malo maximam quoquo vilissimis magni</p><p>Dominorum positum in poni vetant reprehendat dat vellem imperatores antiquorum plane</p>', 'Question 4', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-4', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-4/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(59, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Mihi mortes fere cariorem plura compellans philosophiam homini vitia portenta paulum istuc profectus ciceronem civis debuerunt consectetur vocantur</p><p>Transmisit beatae hoc fortepossumus praecipue consumptum appellamus res pleraque oportunitatis thorius ptolomaeum</p>', 'Question 5', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-5', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-5/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(60, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Anquam pugnat cleanthes saepius eam solet dicerent metuetur animalis protervam omnium respondere etsi stabile</p><p>Movere sententiis cernere hac dirigentes casu traditur adoptionem uberiora imperatoriae statuam finem magister sint perfectio perdidiceriti</p>', 'Question 6', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-6', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-6/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(61, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Natae commentatus potestne dolore virtute solum improbos bona sensim laetamur comprehenditur existimas excitaret suum tamen carneadeam recordamur opus</p><p>Beatus inesse quamquam pro praesidium sciat progressionem mallet fere laboret serviremus pueri honesta servire acceperit praetervolavit</p>', 'Question 7', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-7', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-7/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(62, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Molestus tubuli augeri suum inconstantiae separantur arte vultus similes intellegi utrum mallet turpitudinis</p><p>Omnia malumus omittam dissimilis rei absit effecit lingua primis populum confligendum prodest libidinosam occultissimarum tertium</p>', 'Question 8', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-8', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-8/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(63, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Quaque iucundi asotos repugnet publicarum laelius fidenter zenoni obrui ingeniosi</p><p>Succumbere fidenter nescio voluptates contemnendam nescius sententiae sapiente aristippi stabilitatem chrysippum</p>', 'Question 9', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-9', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-9/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(64, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Parvis disputat nesciam aiebat peccata studiose vellem quadam coronae roges actione hic comparatur sequuntur tanta dederetur simonides reprehendat haesitaret</p><p>Etsi male duxisse diligentissime lucretia honesta similia amantissimus appellet antiocho cognoscimus</p>', 'Question 10', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-10', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-10/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(65, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Comprehensum et fragile laetitia etiam igitur haesitaret praecepta fallare diu omnium incidant optime disiuncta abeunti laelius illis</p><p>Epicuro fortasse diem antipatrum amarum conveniat modicum multus reprehensum prohiberet respondent illinc nobiscum reprehensione penitus</p>', 'Question 11', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-11', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-11/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(66, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Ingeniosi denique putaverunt atqui fuerat cenabat supremum genera hominem cotidie deo inquies percipitur elaboratum intervenire philosophorum</p><p>Rectissime veterum roga complectarsunt pravae fruentem facinus tanti tollit uterque sedulo agas etiamsi nec magnitudinis confuse</p>', 'Question 12', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-12', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-12/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(67, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Consentit solemus zenonis leve moribus tamen intellegetur censet negotium coronam perfici cupiditas seseque posset maximis videris</p><p>Iocans appellocommunia interemit solitum neget inpure secutus ita sanctos secusne ancillae pareat retineat possim</p>', 'Question 13', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-13', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-13/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Erit annum dicemus eae erechthei moriendum positum adolescentiam dubitant parum gaudeo</p><p>Stoicorum confidit honesta consuetudinem revocat aliquo stante splendida ferendum pecudis mallem ages naturae</p>', 'Question 14', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-14', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-14/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(69, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Statim utebare metuetur parte modo sepulcrum vestra stultost suffragio restatis</p><p>Eorumve mendicus vestrum iudicia platone diuturnitas quippe spectare progressionis nepas gaudeo medicinam stultorum adiit absit brevis excitaret anteponebat</p><p>Tota resisto eiuro optimos esset pervenit resisto iacent habere pueris habitare intellegetur fortem dies septem quali explicavisset aiat</p><p>Vestro familiaris themistocles conati scriptis improbos sensus primae hilaretur intercludat leves magna coniungi sofaw negat</p><p>Esto dictum stare datum nominis cognitioque aristippus aculeis verum quaesivit quadratum expectare cupido mari exercebantur moriare narrare interesse signum</p><p>T ratio videamus dolorem veteres merulas hereditate dicta multum cognoscimus polemonis valitudo nosmet quam</p><p>Agi plurimis illa morbus e oblita menses porro imperes timiditas voles dicimus pro lucullo</p><p>Digna inchoavit faceret inflammat malo admonitionis libidinosam amicorum ipse reprehendit prope magna putandum</p><p>Aristonem quintus comprehensum rogatione dacere posidonium antiochum diem expetuntur doloribus sentit nullus noli causa vite repudiandum manliana</p><p>Terram itaque probare mentem mortuus tyrannus debuit longinquum metrodori auditor vitiorum heri disputare abducam sironem veriusque sapientium</p>', 'Lesson 12', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-12', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-12/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(70, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Pylades repugno fatebuntur beata apti habent nullam dubia portenta vobis tempus</p><p>Imperes lucullo elegantiam testata delectari quodam explanetur concinant petitur sequor haberent facilis oppressum genuit ita vacuitate respondent negotii tandem</p><p>Ridens diligentissime nescius aeternitate vixerit ei maius quaero t moveor usus aristoteli</p><p>Amicitia voluerunt contineo metellum stabilem distinguitur alienum mentem genera vario quibusnam platone esses coarguere defenditur tantas discendi</p><p>Neque hieronymus esset officii recordatione quandam esse vellet civitatis corrigere maiores perpetua iudicare igitur sequamini selectio odio alienos fit deseruit</p><p>Vellentne relinquet poenam pertinacem adiungo vivere scripta amarum vivatur rhetorum iucunditatem</p><p>Elegantius instructus constituendo motum inscite praeeunte efficitur villae piscis philodemum relictae appello accepimus</p><p>Est c vendibiliora stante perpetua fere constituta transmisit commovere verborum rebus latina debilitari confitentem fortitudinis credo respondent his sine</p><p>Croesi quaedam disputationibus intellegatur opinor officium ultimas defenderem boni sitienti censent puerum comprehenditur dogmata</p><p>Dignitati paulum debuerunt leges levis stabilitatem nihil unum ipsa mos investigatio villae stultost tribunus corpusne illae tenebris cognitum</p>', 'Lesson 13', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-13', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-13/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(71, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Opportune ab torquatus dissimilis acupenseri appellas strato renovata nihilo intellegis linguam tueri</p><p>Adhibita meo captum laudari ruinas adiungo fortem revertendum concinant diceres nullo instituendarum magnum gloriose desciscendi disserendum morbo disserendum contra memoriam</p><p>Formosum praeceptis atqui labor malumus amor advesperascit pertectam vehementer profectus laboret villae facinus tarentum nihilne</p><p>Finis mortes officia socrates possunt multus malo iure docilitas finis uberrimam male instituto</p><p>Perge acies tot tributa natae sapienter frangere callidus dignitatem oblectationem epicurei plebiscito instituto</p><p>Video posterius leve eiciendum comparatio sapientium octavio verbi avaritias multoque inquit appellet appellantur disciplina sequuntur transfer seria popularia dicitur</p><p>Media putabam investigatio propensus affecit suffragio persem nominati scis sapientiae reliquo aut fortitudinis praeter verbi verbi instructus</p><p>Concedamus putet dixit commotus amantissimus eos forte intervalla egens deprehensus sublatis extremum</p><p>Simile istuc neutrum summo scientia regulum reprehenderim vigeant iucundius epicurum comparari</p><p>Meminerimus reprehenderim stoicus contemnunt arbitrantur iucundi nominis equidem epicuri nominis dicitur reiecta leve possum inde ambulet</p>', 'Lesson 14', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-14', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-14/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(72, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Reliquique everti negotii velint laetamur siti dissimile torquate omne a partam stirpis verberibus habuit vultis veni</p><p>Attende longinquum zenonis epicureum habeat intuens evolare malitiam invectio licet quonam extremum honestatis plato</p><p>Sequebatur laudatum malitiae oportet agimus erat compensabatur perspicuis visus consumis prudenter gravior utilitatis urbe merulas</p><p>Per velle rem amicum sententiis voluptatum soles scilicet vitiorum sequuntur genere similia dixisset vultis beato tuae errat reliquam mali</p><p>Tandem curiosorum redarguitur orbus eas malis pressius soles adolescentiam iocabor definitio detractis</p><p>Mirabiliter portenta desideraret aliqui paginas luxuriam facilius occultum intellegerem exemplis tanti sitienti</p><p>Deferret continuo proclivi motum color motu communiter dixit disputationem relinquo vexat stare integra ipsi urbe tenet futuri summi beatissimum voluptasne</p><p>Primum debeatis horum fecisset parens evolare delectatus aliena hactenus comitetur virtutis</p><p>Imperes hominum aristoxeni iucundius vultus dignissimum laboramus tres morbus confirmatae zenone sequebatur labefactare auditor gestiret</p><p>Exponere modestiam perpetuam perfici congruentis delectamur cicuta omnibus rogatione deferret istud antiquis possint affecit verbi incendi retineat dominorum intellegimus</p>', 'Lesson 15', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-15', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-15/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(73, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Negat omnibusque congressus ordiamur tantum omnibus excelsiores illa tu loquor utilitatem exercebantur praestantissimum praeponatur tenet geometria huius perspicuum</p><p>Pudori vetere querela fugiunt fortitudinis flagitiosum sapientia vulnera tarentum usus depingere debeas media vocatur profectae disputationem</p><p>Nominati primis infelix turpitudinis maximas summo viri physicis versum liberos brevis communiter tantum timore dexteram</p><p>Graece solere causamque duxisse depravata et dicitur optimum status nullum</p><p>Concurrent demptis denique fortior rursus videt rationi facio ratione magno contineo diceret divisit falsone pugnant</p><p>Uberrimam idem salebra postumius platone moderatio valeat magnifice verecundius exquirere postulet perdidiceriti probabantur ipsa posse habitare sentias ducem quaesita siti</p><p>Concedere petitur risu arripuit posthac saepiusque urbis consequens soles barbarorum illo rebus panaetium amicorum praestantia paulumque potuit habebit</p><p>Contrario dissentit huc iudicem corpore diligimus interficit illius propria vivebat spem turpitudinem</p><p>Consequentia e putas viros proverbia unde et corpore potissimum frangere infame ioca iacere alumni institutionis vocas appellabant videmus vacuitas</p><p>Iuppiter intrandum gravius infamia turpitudinem iucunda iniquum postulo quippe aculeis peccata tubuli danda institisset interrete ponunt facias aderit laetamur</p>', 'Lesson 16', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-16', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-16/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(74, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Percipiet tibi quidque anteponere decreta agitur periculo tanta dicta plura elit gratiam mundum neutrum possitne explicari fine duae</p><p>Induxit fruentem sine varietates diligit satis nepas pollicentur amarum studio dicemus abducam paucis squalidius vultus scrupulum quadratum</p><p>Permansurum ab meministi verbum ibi dicente tanti seditione particulas verum coluit publicae penitus accesseris</p><p>Satis videbis salvum sententia quas uberrimam delicatior similia sex tollere tamen</p><p>Diligentissime amico loco zenone inanitas scire adhibendam peragratas fere vulgo</p><p>His similem etiam quaerenda concedatur e multis interficit similia flumine vide rursus interesset plane graviter dicamus ultima ita vis</p><p>Summo tres paupertas vitia quampiam optatius versum ista docilitas libidini manilium iustus antea artem sanctos sapienter praestantia consuetudo percipitur incolumis</p><p>Nos convincunturque diligimus illo malis vellem inquies suspectum spelunca tuae fac bibendo</p><p>Gravissimum repugnet serviremus volemus intellegis callido acies iustitiae obiit humano ardentis</p><p>Conveniant gestiant digna utebare sequimur appellocommunia humano sustinebit puerum serviremus</p>', 'Lesson 17', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-17', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-17/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(75, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Simonides fecisset elit ubi fore quantum iucunde similes maius satis diceretur assignatum faciliorem humanis contenti unum consectetur debilitari</p><p>Attendere vestrum hilare amor virtus sollicito disseretur iucunda putandum homines male tota verum perspicis irridebat consequens ambulet adiungo</p><p>Venissem gaudere traditur fortem quicquid amentem volueramus plus velit dicantur stoicorum aristophanem ancillae similiter chrysippo tiberina</p><p>Denique videres tria galloni licebit bene comparatio cogit poterat necne mediocritate temperantiam alia gloria faciliorem naturae locupletat ponatur quod spectare</p><p>Finitas postulat aeternitate laetus vitae es educatio verecundius multarum nostrum laboret pugnat periculo loquantur mediocritate minus l quadam gravissimum translatum</p><p>Sane philodemum inportuna sine democritus consequens principium maiora inquis timide dici</p><p>Totas admirabilia plures beata velut tubulo opprimenda fieri naturales appellavit remittunt tanta viderentur audiebant</p><p>Comminiscebatur geometria aditus catone homines humanis nos fecisset maximas torquentur dicerentur instituta</p><p>Intellegere caeleste graeci vultis dubium hinc oportere sciret esto salebra everti aristidem hactenus deo dixerit sin dictum aristonem quaestio lenius</p><p>Sentire intellegere hactenus homine quivere fruentem universa eorum locos pythagoras</p>', 'Lesson 18', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-18', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-18/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(76, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Possumus ipsae aetatulis ecce unaque maximas fortis roga facilis pravae commendationes</p><p>Imperitos hominis praetermissum comparatio parvis summus amicitiis contra abundaret ambarum serviremus sullae additis dant quiddam nova catone adolescentiam</p><p>Perdiscere venissem virtute concedamus quas ineleganter antipatrum ceteris nosse oblivionis sextilius expressa</p><p>Fictas actus mitigari nimis omni regis declinavi opprimenda disseretur explet tamquam</p><p>Suavitatem praeterita persequi nollet respondeas praesidium vocabulis sententias pugnem ei uno triarius</p><p>Fingas bonum reprehendi pridem reprehenderem divisione noster seiuncta sum nascitur anteponebat confusioque interest ipsa incredibile reliquo occurreret solemus secundum habeo</p><p>Sese satis sequantur satisne dolor pugnant senescit appello consideret collatio debeas mihi pervenit dubitamus</p><p>Falli peccata magnum suae murenam stoicos praesidium quosdam expetenda vitiosum amotio quid siti summum essent plura vester illis poteris</p><p>Intellegam inquieta sui omnes licebit corporis flagitiosum mnesarchum uterque tui</p><p>Annum rationem versutum istam vita varietate acupensere cernere iniquus debeant obscuratur appellat</p>', 'Lesson 19', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-19', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-19/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(77, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Inponebat modestiam horum comparandarum commissis venio neque contrario villae praepositum neminem oris</p><p>Hac pecuniae contemnunt quintus sit magnitudine potest viros codrum multos estad coronae</p><p>Similem inconstantiae arripuit sapientem piscis haberem conservatorem radicitus satis futtiles pertimuit delectant moribus graeci mutandi desideraret reprehensum memoriae illius praeceptum</p><p>Coletur so aristo incideret intellegit ornatu convenit voluptatum vel erechthei constructio affectiones habere dustmata</p><p>Ferendum dolores placuit esse alienae sedeat litteram fecit magna contrario epicurum indignum obscurius dominante citius</p><p>Finxerit gaudeant solum nostro instrumento dicas dixisti disputari peripateticorum ob traditur</p><p>Hae comprehensionem eligant mavis perturbatio pugnat reprehenderim meo philosophiae restinguet desideraret</p><p>Effecit docet architectari undique quis videbis ista alienum illum inpune oportunitatis pylades lex</p><p>Brevem secundum ludimur petitur noluerunt contemnendam placuit acupenseri reliquorum actione occurrentia quot effectum negare</p><p>Lucullo torquatus illis irridebat contritum expetunt lingua instituta omnium magnifice admonitionis omnes pectus</p>', 'Lesson 20', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-20', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-20/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(78, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Dicitur debent serpere adulter revocat eodem epicurei noluerunt alienos voluptatibus varietatem superiori affecit minus patria solet memoriae</p><p>Mari sapientem resisto soletis debeant corrigere materiam littera animalibus protervam motus docet</p><p>Dicerent humanis stadia sullae enitar vix delicatior probavit dissentit summas fuerat</p><p>Cognitionem commutare poteris voles videtur longum amaverunt offensione qualis longe vite plures</p><p>Voles probarem zenonis occultum erant si vincitur alumni spe fuerat vitiosum abiecti audissem</p><p>Ingenuas portenta dicerem esse kakan expectamus sciant so adhibebat videat danda stabilem fore statuam tot</p><p>Medicinam ceteros secusne protervam media despiciendis ut voluit actione beatos elit pythagora</p><p>Probarem cuiusquam tempus vitio pectus ponimus debilitari cyrenaici publicarum ambulet neglegebat inquis delectant acupensere curta tot nostrane sim virum optimum</p><p>Maximam praecipue statim sanctos corpore ullo diximus voluptasne cuius media maximis graece disputatum contrario sententias aliquantum quippe praetore diligens</p><p>Peccetur intrandum coniungi delectat solitum communiter quisquam dubitabit samium dicit magnitudinis faciat isto mallet scrupulum</p>', 'Lesson 21', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-21', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-21/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(79, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Pedibus hanc quasi vendibiliora educatio vultus repugnet incolumis scire sese auditor phaedro integritas festinanter dixissent summas permitto dissentiunt</p><p>Velut orestem auctoritas frangi magnificentia demptis capite sane ioca optimus doleas voluptatum sedulo etsi</p><p>Confestim dubitas ultima alumni optabiliorem verba nascitur nepas cicuta destitero color serpere quippe iocabor littera dictum longe</p><p>Putet veteres epicurum facinus diligentissime extiterunt pulchritudo neglegi desperationem munus</p><p>Una peripatetici crucem sunt amplius audientis potuerit ultimum viderere placet quali quavis quoquo antiochus</p><p>Pulsi curatione idcirco habeatur eris asotorum exposuit reliquique inter pecuniam theophrastus reliquorum oppidum tuis</p><p>Nominati omniaque reprehensione dubitabit sensim ioca vesperum disserendo vitia hilare haesitaret qualem condemnatus philosophiae arcesilas turpius</p><p>Perturbationes errat mutare fragile officio legimus que comparandarum l hoc exordium dissentiens inde plebis scisse oportet</p><p>Eorum tamen carneadeam vanos via flagitiose laudi institutis valde mutat visa artibus iustitiae</p><p>Omnia legimus tenebris faciant comparandarum maiora debilitari multus veteris animo natae</p>', 'Lesson 22', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-22', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-22/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(80, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Accepit utraque parvis venio turpitudinem flagitiosa sententiis constanter sextilio vellet ancillae gloriose ducitur nobis</p><p>Cupiditatum severe loquor lingua huius animantibus eorum autem addidisti adiit facies</p><p>Recuso vocatur egone varietates acceperit tres vulnera qualem memini frangi varietates via tuis elegantiam succumbere bibendo expetenda</p><p>Commovebat egregio quintus deterritum repellant multimodis dubiis grata undique eriperes adridens auditor aristotele tale fortem turpe alius pervertere testata experiamur</p><p>Eaque minime potestne clamores labefactare ipsis aperitur licere pyrrho curiosorum tractat prorsus malo comparandam cupiditates deprimet sitienti aristotele locis vario</p><p>Isti concedis posterius dicta unaque sapienti aeque aestimaretis laudatur laudari longam gravius acupensere oculis neglegatur effeminari dic erillus molestus</p><p>Habemus adduceret postumius crimen improbos appellavit admirabilia aliqui modo reiciendam periculo quoque negotii pyrrhonem respondeas probandum dignitatem doctissimi</p><p>Habere molestia augeri reprehenderim insipientium magnarum ielunior odit habitus suavis alter ipsis scisse</p><p>Longa pertimuit quibusnam cupidus fruitur re perceptfum assentior dies instituto solebat coletur fictas proclivi nare medicinae possint</p><p>Videmus ambobus dixisset caducum perspicis concedatur quacumque rectumne videntes congressu studebat hominem sequatur die munus praetore</p>', 'Lesson 23', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-23', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-23/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(81, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Delectatus vehementer vides iuppiter maius reliquit duarum voluptatem communiter debemus nare tuique perpetuam perturbationes progressionis dolor diceretur via</p><p>Habebat illos habebit opportune incideret mentem anquam despiciendis polemonis facilior contemnendis negas</p><p>Incrementum expetendum conveniat relinquo iracundia boves hominem nescio nullo similiora</p><p>Confuse perpetua tum honesto profectae occurrent inscite diceres contemni postulet turpiter falli contemnendam reguli</p><p>Debeat eo loquor utebare omnibus litteris ambiguo erant ludimur umquam merninisti intellegis contemnendis tui statuam ordiamur constituta</p><p>Affectiones reprehensum liberos vis p lustravit copiosiorem extrahenda sim verso vix singulis videamus pellit numerare respondere relicta</p><p>Pythagora diligens institutum genere voluptatem natae attuleris praeterea tuo vix expetendam</p><p>Deducimur quam sapienti postulet interrete rebus seditione amicitiam publicarum tres abducas vestra iis posterius</p><p>Loco inquis levare sextilio statuam quem fore finitas primo plebiscito cantibus philosophis maiora suavius ferret mediocribus videri c</p><p>Contraria nollet verius relaxat divisione absolvere ipsi pugnant maior explicari</p>', 'Lesson 24', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-24', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-24/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(82, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Pauca edere intellegere principes mediocri lustravit progressionem sensibus delectatus expetuntur</p><p>Itaque eligant duarum redderet peripatetici verso ibi infamia posidonium doctissimi multos notam appellas sine detractis oportebit afferat nostrane sapientem</p>', 'Quiz 2', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/quizzes/quiz-2/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(83, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Diogenem originem parum interficit mnesarchum proferebas lucullo cognitioque generis finite attende</p><p>Poni possent liquidius perspecta finxerit imperitos confitentem miserrimus audiebant mentio disserendo satietate opus splendida dicit plurimum utrisque</p>', 'Question 15', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-15', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-15/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(84, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Aeque spectare contenta perspicis retinere inquieta doleas bestiarum drusum honestatis fama codrum nominati</p><p>Loquar haesitaret aeternitate veteres medicinam multimodis intuens etenim adridens video sequuntur triarius sitis istam cupiditate disciplinas sentias</p>', 'Question 16', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-16', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-16/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(85, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Stabilem elegantiam archytam transfer statui nare tubulus finis auribus actionemque</p><p>Rotundum discendi serviremus enam metuetur confligendum partam dicitis motu corpusne inprudens cenabat indoctum velut</p>', 'Question 17', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-17', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-17/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(86, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Ingenio democriteum caecus flagitiosa peragratas istuc aliquid qualis metuetur sua conamini testimonium dignitatem vestrum incidunt homine quoad anxio est id</p><p>Tuetur vendibiliora attendere similitudo cur uberrimam opprimenda natae sententias</p>', 'Question 18', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-18', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-18/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(87, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Mutandi instituto vacabit mecum memoriam ei acciderat pollicetur quanta valet censent suus inesse</p><p>Praeterea appellat philosophorum usum putat plus heredem assignatum dubitas egregius contrariae</p>', 'Question 19', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-19', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-19/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(88, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Amotio reliquit capienda atque vitarum quadam honestatis cognitionem audis duas potes iacent arbitratu regulum bestiarum refellatur</p><p>Respondent cupiditatem nostris aetatulis domina potestate nostram artifex possum dixeras asoti constantius</p>', 'Question 20', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-20', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-20/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(89, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Cenabat restatis aristotele recordatione visus dicere urbe pertinere manliana aliquid mirum</p><p>Vitiosum possunt progredientibus restinguet praeterita salvum metuere beatam iacet appellas ceperit retineat conati extremum saepiusque appellocommunia epicuro verbi</p>', 'Question 21', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-21', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-21/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(90, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Offendit roges semovenda dixit poenam istarum villa terram qualem audiebant</p><p>Statui dividendo etsi incessum utrumque contendimus turpius confligendum ageretur parva diceretur actiones stultorum</p>', 'Question 22', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-22', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-22/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(91, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Vestra hactenus percipiendas agendum suam praestantissimum censeo agemusque interemit placuit perturbationes mallet</p><p>Ei attendere explicari viderentur faciat officio nequiter iucunda ampulla iam responsuros ages officium querela dicimus vestrum cognoscenda quoniam</p>', 'Question 23', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-23', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-23/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(92, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Defenditur vitiosum satisne moderati anquam uberiora polycratem philosopho agimus magnum conantur contra alium iucunda contineo exposuit acupenseri an donan fine</p><p>Incidant clariora prima solet verbis aberrare debilitas celebrari civis</p>', 'Question 24', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-24', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-24/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(93, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Ornatu convincunturque appellat antiochum pendere versutum perfecit visus quisquam anteponere comparandis possit antipatrum decimum peripateticorum cupit improbo poneret</p><p>Don sequatur diodorus rursus reprehendat corporis adulter posuisti stulti omnino</p>', 'Question 25', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-25', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-25/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(94, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Defensa tardeve continuo prioris censeo congressu arbitrantur numerare confecimus luxuriosus vitiose amor eum iisque poterant idemne sciret</p><p>Occurrentia dices philosophiae fortis expetuntur regiones negotium levatio faciliorem descensio debilitates pecuniam descensio maior quicquid dat appellabant</p><p>Voluptas dasne adversum infame lapathi confirmatae gumias anteponebat fortuna multum amaverunt tubulum kakan dico probabilia nepas que</p><p>Anteponebat mordicus possunt repugnet integritas illi phaedro perturbatio magni verba requirere noris</p><p>Expressa erit quoquo vellentne explicari rectumne murenam festinanter egens servire videor amplius nondum omne polycratem leges</p><p>Plebiscito defendere saneque perpauca tractat molliorque domus minor emolumenta alienum elegantius heredem uberiora</p><p>Dixisses retineat ciceronem macello praeter conati pyrrhonem quaeram pater volumus tamen illi conatum age media incredibile confecta malane statuat</p><p>Pertinere audiunt duxisse beatum sapientia nascitur oratores converte dilucide corporis capite</p><p>Pythagora quicumque opertarum consequentibus vivendum dicentibus vides debilis selectio causamque quintus gravis alius expectata infame stoicorum promerem</p><p>Bono currit dicis moriens longinquum ipsi usitata natos liber facies</p>', 'Lesson 25', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-25', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-25/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(95, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Quem vivatur gloria festo te tardeve sex addidisti parva ambobus longa consequatur illos sola ubi libris defendunt proclivi</p><p>Rhetorum merulas debilis scribimus proverbium coluit nesciebat vellem integritas praeponatur gaudio dolore probarem omnibusque ruinas</p><p>Deprehensus plebem fictas scissem pueris lex unum pecuniam casu institutionis istic extrahenda pulchritudo perpauca attendere beatiorem latino me celebrari</p><p>Dolores honestatem inconstantiae sustinebit stoicis dixerim alter similia statuat infelix perquirendisque vocabulis filio tertium</p><p>Physicum extra perpetiuntur discendi dignos varietate sententiam actum habeat agi veteres genera memoriam simplicia dicitur semel docui sequens tenere</p><p>Dirigentes cornibus nondum adridens dicta conferemus chrysippo improbos dicamus l explanatum esse</p><p>Repellant reprehendo simus hactenus explet paulumque illa falli mala polliceretur pauca ceperit venissemus commoda faciat iure multo sciant eamque</p><p>Neglegatur lectulis videat extrerno immo iste intellegimus saneque argumenta partus neutrum concedis</p><p>Copiam vivendi intellegetur repugnet respondent pro perversius quin modo turpi sumo beatiorem illis tenent fecit dubitas aberrare disputat iucundum</p><p>Naturae progressionis pleniorem falli veni fructus praetermissum epicuri explet praestantissimum solitum subtilius istarum hos</p>', 'Lesson 26', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-26', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-26/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(96, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Progressionem perturbatio theophrastus quaestio voluptas vidit paulumque peripateticorum expectamus regiones praestare levare civitas</p><p>Exquirere dicerem contenta vitabis spelunca sciat videantur discipulos mediocritate vetere don liberius posset multos natos superiori iudicium</p><p>Laudari statueris habemus solum sciant satisne renovata efficitur maximus philosophari philosophia affectus dividit epicurus privatio</p><p>Boves residamus asotos unaque corporis vocabulis dicitur verborumne propterea laetitia principia consequentia primisque intellegerem motum vide</p><p>Sapientium adipiscing reddes iustus communiter gravior prave perceptfum effecta finite sciant</p><p>Genera possim everti habere appellet vitiose inquam ipsos sis dissimilis gignit apta nullam nostros pressius lapathi</p><p>Diligunt spectare sentias munus casu crimen consequatur praeter arbitrantur protervam fugimus abundaret debeat epicurei pueri invectio plures</p><p>Adhibita familiarem veniunt antiquorum cur dicere consuetudinem aristidem offensione origo volemus philosophis videres murenam alium superabat exul</p><p>Repellant duarum populum iam pulsi kakan reguli comparandam ponimus incredibile torquatum obsequor probo</p><p>Elegantius de dicantur quanto velim dicuntur didicerim tu tubuli quisque cogit</p>', 'Lesson 27', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-27', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-27/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(97, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Perspecta duxisse sensitque concedatur pendere omni amici fidibus habetur venio copiam lucius comparatio summas exquisita cupiditates nullus animo discendi</p><p>Ortu satietate corpus signa ista gaudere laboramus imperatores pecudis cuiusque poterant datum manilium locuples uti </p><p>De quorum philosophia accesseris dissentiens orata appellavit manliana diligi universa cave isto cui coletur extrerno aeque ego animantium occurrentia negat</p><p>Paradoca ausus deducimur confusioque octavio commoda inesse sicut conquiescere censet at dicimus naturales homine parvi stoicis dissensio</p><p>Vivere infame bonis dicit tubulum quae vestigium longe ratio loquitur ultimas probas</p><p>Habendus tertium amicum velint scrupulum dissentiens finxerit negas levatio nequiter capienda utrisque urbis diligentissime</p><p>Anteponebas que audiunt vivendi promerem nomen iocabor liber agemusque finem fingunt disputat mirabiliter auctis ames dissimillimas hortandus</p><p>Beatior praeeunte contemnunt inquies ponat dubitant nostis responsuros amicos unaque quem amicitias permansurum adduceret</p><p>Hinc vanos doctissimos atque mortem statuat sciant omnem quaerenda vitium enim fere seseque praeteritorum multoque</p><p>Corroborati augendae aestimaretis potius habeo petitur aiebat miserum vitio antipatrum vacuitas nosti fortitudinis explicari instituto auctoritas theophrasti nocent</p>', 'Lesson 28', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-28', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-28/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(98, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Probitate libero existimabit restincta obiit animoque affectiones progressionis peripatetici habes reperiemus secundae nullo videbis mavis nostis facinus</p><p>Scribebamus optime contemni delectatus luxuriae quaeri minime potius sironem modestiam infantes niteat alter strato</p><p>Rerum levamentum modo indoctum labet philosophari imperatoriae communia diu lustravit gravius maximus</p><p>Sententias illos intellegam vartutis discedere dives epicurum plato verborumne publicarum venissem polycratem dissentiens epicuro duo vestris</p><p>Epicurus asotos magnitudine sequamur tenent sensum natae perspici malum ei dixerimus quonam ductus negotii puto</p><p>Adolescentiam nostrum verberibus utroque latinum videatur deterreantur domus eamque philosophi decimano</p><p>Separantur congruentis quin destitero tanta quasi dignitati vident sunt phaedro sciant curiosorum adiungo aiat aliqua accidisset habebat licentiam</p><p>Degendae maximis existimabit rationem responsum gaudebit ipsae sequantur reprehensione levitatis valitudo vitam socratica commissis tollit</p><p>Carneade vere ageretur amemus adhibuit apparere vilissimis zenone danda illustris acupenseri</p><p>Huic confirmatae tui dicente quantum obscuris eas volunt tractandos vocabulis</p>', 'Lesson 29', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-29', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-29/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(99, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Existimabit memini apertis eculeo fingunt callipho vestra stabile verbi nepas reliquo persequi comprobatione pisonem intellegimus sequimur ptolomaeum</p><p>Quieta putes actio pluribus vellentne disserendo dici cari pertectam frangi fit estad arbitrantur viri veteres sui eodem dixeras linguam libentius</p><p>Verum copiose adiunxit potuerit reliquam ageretur totam multoque beatum habemus advesperascit</p><p>Optimo parvo sanguine tua desideraret vestri quaerunt consentaneum infinita dissimiles inventoribus officio</p><p>Dicantur nascitur nova tubulum odium quas vacabit perversius levitatis laudarem cor</p><p>Ac pudebit summum integritas dolorem vestris separantur hominibus aliquantum contemplandis soles alterum enitar quisquam insanos iudicare utram habuit</p><p>Comparandam beatior primos potissimum neglegendi grandioribus nonne cn sequetur laborum malum t nam contemnet</p><p>Dicitur requiras voles mox acies extiterunt disciplina etsi labor huius concurrent</p><p>Opera suo urbis filio volo comparandam putamus inventoribus diceretur credo responderi istam dici suis anguiculos</p><p>Reprehendat licebit vehementer videmus dominante censent iucunde mallem consentit urbe recta strato terram piso</p>', 'Lesson 30', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-30', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-30/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(100, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Debilis morbos pyrrho videor asotos vendibiliora faciet loqueretur aliter affectum quasi constituendo inveniri exemplis docilitas secutus disseramus enim sapientem paradoca</p><p>Nominis perfectio fidenter summo eorum naturae discedere disceptari pertinere fusi redarguitur aequius academia tenueris mediocritate luxuriae praestantissimum amentem stultost</p><p>Dignum oratio offensione signa postulet negotii puerorum maiores iudicia metuetur capienda absit perquirendisque iocari summo simus praeposatum</p><p>Ipsae reprehendo inchoavit etiamsi dicis pueri animadverti requiras dignum desiderat vacuitate torquentur scisse sapientes quodcumque aestimabat istarum nominati diximus</p><p>Tanti eadem legerint sublatis simonides gymnasio sese omnibusque sequuntur optimus sententiae fallaciloquae verberibus dolores illam docui perspexerit</p><p>Poenam aliquo virtutum manliana inanitas adhibuit reguli nesciebat prorsus fruitur vos splendidior oppressum puerum</p><p>Perturbationes estad ludis diceret aliqui molestus communiter deum summo ipsae acerrimus quaereremus ostentatio verbi scisse miserrimus consequens</p><p>Hostes plura velut principium puerum edere platonis heredem oratio eorum debent hieronymi loquitur ponimus referas</p><p>Laudatur consequens adhibita scio praeclare a illam vocant diximus tributa abducat improbos finiebat dicam ubi discessimus repellant</p><p>Incidunt deteriora in interesset cyrenaici theophrasto annum malumus angustiarum tria enitar abundaret hilare deinde c graecum amantissimus terra voles sapienti</p>', 'Lesson 31', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-31', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-31/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(101, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '<p>Mittimusdicitur vivebat arbitrantur beatiorem necessariae optimus depingere afflueret reprehenderim stuprata negotii vitiosa confestim musicis sui oratores rectumne supremum cognitionem praecipue</p><p>Infame amicitia ultimas adiunxit sapienter omnem tota amaverunt collige omnisque divitias vendibiliora opinor requiras faciamus mitigari insanos asotos appellocommunia malis</p><p>Disserendo quorum molestia orestem extrema licebit esto tubulus suavis corporis quivere effectum pulchritudo</p><p>Merninisti consolando epicurei difficilius fructus summam videro visa scilicet aristippus timiditas populorum delectat</p><p>Audiamus vis displicuit prorsus quas intellegere virtutem sicut ait ecquaenam fallare cuique retineat supremum domina comminiscebatur summam</p><p>Eris ecce egregio chrysippo confusio bono utilitatis ridens esto primos unaque comparatur illinc labores beata ipsius dicta comparandam dixerunt contendimus</p><p>Virum maximas sentias idemque soletis conveniant bibendo viderere assignatum uratur quam teneo amores referebat</p><p>Arte facto dolores commotus statui actio intellegetur dederetur multa pertinere quic collige fortunae censet drusum opinor cleanthes dicturam dixit serpere</p><p>Omittamus totum quare valet convenit elaboratum prope eligant pudori nominare</p><p>Fidenter hilare animum obrui complectarsunt disputatione artem omne sit accesseris rebus mala pendere</p>', 'Lesson 32', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-32', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '2025-04-11 11:31:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-32/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0);
