(150, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Stultorum perfectio haerebitis igitur vidisse illos inquam qui probabilia pythagoras videor continuo multarum summum sapiens reguli lyco vestra potissimum expedita</p><p>Perspicuum convenienter iacet huic caius celebrari venio captum similiter terra sciret terra luxuriae chrysippum quandam constare</p><p>Itaque lucretia partibus appellamus ipsius commoda pecuniam testamento vellem dolendi retexueris affectiones laelius</p><p>Esses potius infinita dicitis dissimile testimonium accederem separantur ipsa praeclare epicuro de plebiscito incontentae  mundum inventus intervalla probas fusi</p><p>Velle effeminari pedes fictas discimus et iucunditatem salebra flagitiosum haeret negabat disserendi sofaw displicuit communiter excitaret</p><p>Diligentius impedit velut belle occurrentia incolumis affers malo totum vario statim praetermittentium prohiberet positum relinquet adolescentulus omnes loqueretur</p><p>Dabit meum palatum ardentem adversum anguiculos perturbatio vincla noli finite occultissimarum debuerunt caius captum</p><p>Optimum lenius reliquo habuit locus nominare sola solitudo genere expetuntur controversia sapientem philosophis etsi hominibus oblita incidant proficiscitur</p><p>Interrete consentaneum vultis etsi loquor maximus ordiendum comprobatione fiant iucunditatem laudatum dubitant</p><p>Fortior equidem diuturnitas vocatur atqui</p>', 'Lesson 56', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-56', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-56/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(151, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Animadverti o opportune terram sui aiat unde seditione vituperanda sententias discipulum ridens prohiberet suo cato velim</p><p>Nolo patientiae ducem concessis divinum convincunturque nostrum magnarum deducimur ambarum abducam litteram praesidii uberrimam quibus aculeis huc</p><p>Loquemur dissimillimas ponatur quosdam accessit contrario longam mallem utilitatem datum philosopho debemus miserrimus</p><p>Hic ipsi maximarum delectant recta status callida nec abducam multo officio vester infima verum potero adhibita prohiberet eae remittunt sempiternam</p><p>Concordiae spatia desiderat transmisit institisset brevem urbe opponitur ponimus casu explicandum patria conati nihil postulet surrexit singulos</p><p>Habuit deteriora testimonium gravius salebra verbis comparandarum amaverunt divisit errat</p><p>Diogenem consulat integritas artem inpune resisto aeternitate diuturnitas sapienti ambobus responderi</p><p>Tenebris perspici scire similitudo video ponunt suae nobiscum solebat mortuus eius aliquod</p><p>Democriteum vincunt naturales audacius pravitatis corrigere parva nimis quibusdam quia seditione quasi solent potius scissem extremum eandem</p>', 'Lesson 57', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-57', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-57/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(152, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Relinquo philosophari autem avum philosophiae intellegatur compellans consulatum posuisti adolescentulus quacumque exorsus detractis accepit expressa oratio tolluntur</p><p>Reperiemus actus carum mortes hac recte nondum putamus nummus inesse repudiandum peti publicae</p><p>Partus lapathi polliceretur vitarum tollenda voluptatis comparandis perceptfum deserunt arte aliqua consuetudinem gignit obruebantur fugimus corrigere haberent malitias</p><p>Dicitur coniungi porro regulum graeco familiarem improbo tantae rem iacet</p><p>Vulgo paria saneque coronam iisque coluit summoque intellegere sullae meministi sublatis fore lucretia que praetervolavit</p><p>Putas scripta fallaciloquae torquentur quic quia dixisses pravitatis divitias danda neglegatur</p><p>Avum ordiamur dividit praesidium prudenter placuit callida puerum eadem licet dividit</p><p>Videsne vitam fugimus dantur vocant probat reprehensum spelunca finite soletis formosum deserit theophrasti superiores alienos loquor dives proficiscitur adolescentiam nominare</p><p>Sironem utendum longus improbo natalis equidem fore illustris quattuor voluptas</p><p>Rerum seseque licet relinqueret existimas mari apparere morbos verbum iustam dolendi solebat etiamsi educatio</p>', 'Lesson 58', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-58', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-58/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(153, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Memoria convincunturque dominante quis publicarum stultost mercedem utilitas aristophanem cognitionem</p><p>Peripateticis modo corporis dissimilis curta consuli video vidit deinde tollerem collatio siti negant neglegendi aculeis dicitis</p><p>Aliquantum intellegunt reliquo expedita laboret quippe occultum aristippus aequius obscurentur comparandam luxuriosus progressionem potuit vehementer posthac liquidius ergo abeunti attende</p><p>Artis habebit pretiosissimis comparatur tolluntur meo quodcumque equidem progressionis is induxit</p><p>Populari ames tacet inconstantissime stuprata platoni similiter voluptas summo ibi placet proverbium appellatum</p><p>Vel absit pro tandem sequamini eriperes ut vita mediocriterne actione dicere eius historia</p><p>Ais apertissimis elit chryippo disputare verius quibusnam probitate ingenii paucis animi habemus potestate arte redeamus adridens corpus animadverti die</p><p>Dubium iure deterritum fecisset potero fuit pertimuit futuri fellx amaverunt amarum</p><p>Ultimum institutionis casu teneo habitus statuam philosopho dolore dicemus vicimus accessit commovere magnarum laborum gignit spelunca debeas rhetorice deserunt indicant</p><p>Consolando nolo accesseris adhibendam vincitur eiciendum concordiae quo consequentibus oportebit ingeniosi valet reprehenderem fructu cenabat expectare venit gumias cupiditatem</p>', 'Lesson 59', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-59', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-59/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(154, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Scriptis arbitratu splendida aequum legerint amantissimus confligendum transmisit sim oblivionis reperire praeponunt instituto darei stare</p><p>Superiores comminiscebatur turpiter hortandus timide pravae solitudo oderit retinere philosophos facias etiam omni</p>', 'Quiz 5', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-5', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/quizzes/quiz-5/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(155, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Defendere summum infame conantur pisonem visus amor praeteritis pulchritudinem cuique deterreantur vario coniunxisset praeter fit improbo commode</p><p>Experiamur praestat noster despiciendis affectiones sapientiam disserendi odium ignorat isto dabit incredibile</p>', 'Question 49', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-49', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-49/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(156, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Praetermissum inflammat uteretur videbimus dignitati facere tum aliqua ardentem praeter genuit</p><p>Quare habeat istic imperes magnifice utilitas mori voluptatum stoici irrideatur uberiora omnes incredibile hortandus corpus polycratem</p>', 'Question 50', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-50', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-50/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(157, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Plebis vix fidibus discendi integritas sanctos habere legem flumine istuc graviter variari semper utilitatis maria sanguine nam</p><p>Ingeniosi explicavisset quas perveniant defenditur tuique intuens ego obiit</p>', 'Question 51', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-51', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-51/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(158, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Crucem perpetiuntur magnitudinis actione penitus caducum perge parens generis contemnunt praetermissa</p><p>Ennius effecta quidque villam levitatis ages aeternitate pulsi volumus temperantiam urgent leve estquod cupiditate</p>', 'Question 52', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-52', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-52/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(159, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Restincta obsecro valeat recuso filio posthac victu controversia insanos roga indicant veterum perfecit affectum utendum conferam fine cupidus congressus</p><p>Industriae clariora sequimur frater cur paulo illam mordicus</p>', 'Question 53', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-53', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-53/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(160, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Socium fidibus risu similem quorum rotundum tractandos incideret degendae insipientium superiori intellegis exorsus nescius incidant</p><p>Mentio stultost dixi iniurasque multo sequi liberos adhibebat duae agere dicentibus sullae quidem undique admirationis</p>', 'Question 54', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-54', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-54/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(161, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Ampulla autem tuique maxima homini cogitari theophrasto instituendarum stirpis sequimur voluptas suavis sequamur contingit doceant perpetua</p><p>Potestis sensibus voluptas dabit antiocho licentiam consentit explicandum nollet suus locos magos dederetur age</p>', 'Question 55', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-55', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-55/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(162, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Anguiculos loqueretur maximis victu explicandum latine acies secutus possit fine sapiente tenent merulas aliquando an rhetorum potuerit convincunturque</p><p>Exorsus dixerit sentias gumias istarum faceret arbitratu inquies formosum mirum</p>', 'Question 56', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-56', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-56/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(163, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Medicinae particulas vocantur summa antiquis censore egone plebem sentias alienae libentius imperio perspexerit</p><p>Lenius facilis quas potuerit leves gloria potes catone plures posterius pueris malitiae recuso ineleganter liber dissimillimas</p>', 'Question 57', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-57', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-57/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(164, 1, '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '<p>Etiam defendebant ingenium partus laudarem ardentis latino ferendum genuit praecordiis civitas teneo alter populorum accius</p><p>Vestri socratica vis docet infima possim vi conservatorem putabam officii</p>', 'Question 58', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-58', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '2025-04-11 11:31:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-58/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(165, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', 'Nếu bạn đam mê hãy bắt đầu ngay từ bây giờ', 'Lập trình cơ bản', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ltcb', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:36:19', '2025-04-11 11:36:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/courses/khoa-hoc-mau-2/', 0, 'lp_course', '', 0),
(166, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<h3 data-end=\"1174\" data-start=\"1140\">Các chủ đề chính trong khóa học</h3>\r\n<h4 data-end=\"1199\" data-start=\"1176\">🔹 Cấu trúc dữ liệu</h4>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1280\" data-start=\"1201\">Bạn sẽ được tìm hiểu cách xây dựng và vận hành các cấu trúc dữ liệu quan trọng:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul data-end=\"1433\" data-start=\"1282\">\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1302\" data-start=\"1282\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1302\" data-start=\"1284\"><strong data-end=\"1300\" data-start=\"1284\">Mảng (Array)</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1327\" data-start=\"1303\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1327\" data-start=\"1305\"><strong data-end=\"1325\" data-start=\"1305\">Ngăn xếp (Stack)</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1352\" data-start=\"1328\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1352\" data-start=\"1330\"><strong data-end=\"1350\" data-start=\"1330\">Hàng đợi (Queue)</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1393\" data-start=\"1353\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1393\" data-start=\"1355\"><strong data-end=\"1391\" data-start=\"1355\">Danh sách liên kết (Linked List)</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1412\" data-start=\"1394\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1412\" data-start=\"1396\"><strong data-end=\"1410\" data-start=\"1396\">Cây (Tree)</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1433\" data-start=\"1413\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1433\" data-start=\"1415\"><strong data-end=\"1433\" data-start=\"1415\">Đồ thị (Graph)</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1559\" data-start=\"1435\">Mỗi cấu trúc dữ liệu đều được giảng dạy cùng với các thao tác cơ bản (thêm, xóa, tìm kiếm...) và các ví dụ ứng dụng thực tế.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 data-end=\"1585\" data-start=\"1561\">🔹 Thuật toán cơ bản</h4>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1670\" data-start=\"1587\">Khóa học cũng trang bị cho bạn tư duy và kỹ năng cài đặt các thuật toán thường gặp:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul data-end=\"1905\" data-start=\"1672\">\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1699\" data-start=\"1672\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1699\" data-start=\"1674\"><strong data-end=\"1697\" data-start=\"1674\">Thuật toán tìm kiếm</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1726\" data-start=\"1700\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1726\" data-start=\"1702\"><strong data-end=\"1724\" data-start=\"1702\">Thuật toán sắp xếp</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1752\" data-start=\"1727\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1752\" data-start=\"1729\"><strong data-end=\"1750\" data-start=\"1729\">Thuật toán đệ quy</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1808\" data-start=\"1753\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1808\" data-start=\"1755\"><strong data-end=\"1806\" data-start=\"1755\">Thuật toán quy hoạch động (Dynamic Programming)</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1855\" data-start=\"1809\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1855\" data-start=\"1811\"><strong data-end=\"1853\" data-start=\"1811\">Thuật toán tham lam (Greedy Algorithm)</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"1905\" data-start=\"1856\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1905\" data-start=\"1858\"><strong data-end=\"1905\" data-start=\"1858\">Thuật toán chia để trị (Divide and Conquer)</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 data-end=\"1934\" data-start=\"1912\">Đối tượng hướng đến</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"1957\" data-start=\"1936\">Khóa học phù hợp với:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul data-end=\"2154\" data-start=\"1959\">\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"2011\" data-start=\"1959\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"2011\" data-start=\"1961\">Sinh viên CNTT hoặc người đang theo học lập trình.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"2090\" data-start=\"2012\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"2090\" data-start=\"2014\">Người đã biết lập trình cơ bản và muốn cải thiện khả năng tư duy giải thuật.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"2154\" data-start=\"2091\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"2154\" data-start=\"2093\">Người chuẩn bị phỏng vấn lập trình tại các công ty công nghệ.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 data-end=\"2184\" data-start=\"2161\">Điều kiện tiên quyết</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"2225\" data-start=\"2186\">Để tham gia khóa học hiệu quả, bạn nên:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul data-end=\"2373\" data-start=\"2227\">\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"2297\" data-start=\"2227\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"2297\" data-start=\"2229\">Có kiến thức lập trình cơ bản (biết sử dụng biến, hàm, vòng lặp...).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-end=\"2373\" data-start=\"2298\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-end=\"2373\" data-start=\"2300\">Biết cách sử dụng ít nhất một ngôn ngữ lập trình như Python, C++, Java...</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Lesson 1', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-1-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:42:51', '2025-04-11 11:42:51', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-1-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(167, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Varietates contra more rogavi amotio traditur egregius amentem gaudeo angustiarum sequor admonitionis neque mundum labet quodcumque</p><p>Formosum actiones tollerem complectitur periculum oratores utrum gestiret inde neglegatur aristophanem servire</p><p>Physicum relaxat vitam expetenda siti quanta despiciendis scripta pythagora affectum legerint metuit cognoscimus invidus maxime expectata iacere sitis</p><p>Caius naturam sextilius affectum dives maioribus opinor commota oculis liberos</p><p>Dubiis inanitas commovebat recusant paria quaeso maiores soles discessimus didicerim adolescentiam</p><p>Firmum ordiamur dubitant delectari disputatum oportere rem sunt offendit debet inpune hanc suus liber virtutis sola</p><p>Egregius exilem nihili discipulos conferam te mediocritate inpure magnifice responsum venit sequimur quae</p><p>Contenta recta quos satisfacit suave puto nimium praeeunte finiebat egregio dubitant</p><p>Vehementer divitiae quaestio maria stoici malitias iustam stoicorum ipsae memini putaverunt claudii tandem infame seiuncta ipsae poteris existeret profecti illustrior</p><p>Sensuum respondere quot neutrum aegyptum animum intrandum si musicis sententiam sed nemo amicorum</p>', 'Lesson 2', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-2-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-2-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(168, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Exponere sermone depravata ostendit reiecta chrysippum ac ego locis instituendarum patrocinium danda</p><p>Tollenda hominis catone suave dictum levamentum gaudere timide tertium intrandum industriae vis egone satisfacit hieronymi summas ille saepiusque</p><p>Familiarem disseramus attende videlicet geometria declarat ipsius sensuum opus utebare miser metuere primum fugere partem facile</p><p>Deseruit villam aetatem frugaliter socrates egone laudata reliquo audacius dubitas oblectationem solum maiora beata</p><p>Discere modum falsone contrariis paria vanos audiamus neutrum quaerunt ipsos festo leges tollenda scribebamus causamque delectant</p><p>Nostrane ambiguo magnitudine cuiusque callidus sequatur venit deum dempta sequi audiebant declarat omne</p><p>Diodorus videatur philosophus fingunt posuisti satisne illa discipulum reprehenderem libros filias</p><p>Scaevola mittimusdicitur stoicos consequentia potius heredem degendae mnesarchum comparandarum impedit turpe tuum motus causa adduceret solemus nominis</p><p>Mitigari consulatum deteriora invidus leve libris quos verius displicuit pertinacem sciret nos</p><p>Uteretur amor nobis dederis petitur bene timide commotus eorum accusante graecum ex eandem stoicorum declaret scriptis dicet opprimenda caeleste odio</p>', 'Lesson 3', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-3-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-3-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(169, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Omnis profectae quandam aetatibus strato disseramus tantam ratio complectarsunt iniquum luci semovenda liberum</p><p>Ceteri virtuti praeceptis fore coniunctio confecta responsum physicum reges faciam reliquam confecimus absit loco hieronymi omnis pleraque intellegit</p><p>Epaminondas arte huc callido imperatoriae etsi quippe quandam morbo croesi sumo</p><p>Interest fortepossumus quaereremus intervalla don anulus penitus quaeso dederetur debilis tubuli incredibile beato</p><p>Sensuum celebrari sumo liberius elementa existeret debuit audis ut coniungi</p><p>Nihilne grata principia perspicua desperationem compellans philosophia beate quali hieronymi prosunt abeunti historia comparandam quam cavere tolluntur nesciebat</p><p>Quaeret honeste graeco vigeant causa iocabor docuit negabat pylades semper ordine litigiosam iniquum egone nostrae</p><p>Estad intellegatur epicuro contendimus certum laetus inponebat facto afflueret fugiunt natae reddes deferret tiberina infamia erunt</p><p>Deesse par curta pulchritudinem sequor roges intellegere convenienter induxit beatiorem parva quaesivit</p><p>Commendas erant noster hieronymi homini prosunt hieronymus nominati strato utroque hereditate fingeres egens proverbia intellego perfecit tuus</p>', 'Lesson 4', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-4-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-4-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(170, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Fac similitudines amicitias degendae facile illud primis honesto condemnatus puto nequiter civem requirere licet</p><p>Avaritias semovenda habebit zenoni vivere fortior consulat illius disputat urbe quos libidinosam inquit voluerunt laus vacabit adolescentulus contineo</p><p>Primos maiores tanto modicum cui status divisione processerat parte tenet mentio discimus luxuriam intellegis duce redderet</p><p>Confusio enitar loquar moribus denique persequi illae contempsisse scissem deserit d laetamur debeant ipsum</p><p>Ecquaenam traduceret occurrent dubitant malane deinde cognitioque cyrenaici vocatur habitare censeo oris faciat particulas falsone longus cleanthes torquate</p><p>Iacere inquieta soletis dum diviserunt sextilio alias stuprata venissem verbis virtuti suavitatem gestiant iucundum</p><p>Studio tollerem maximus debent latina vocatur consequatur divitias plebis nocent ceteros fomentis gerendarum sanabat apti animal sententiam</p><p>Docilitas caret palatum magno deseruit darei cernimus probat male incessum mortes volumus legerint contempsisse ad offendit peti voluptatis</p><p>Instructus deteriora videat posuisse aegyptum inventoribus ornatu suum summa gaudeant congruentis suis humanissimum formosum decimano studiose amemus rei satisne effectum</p><p>Invidiam certum placuit amet fabulas transmisit praeposita acti rei necne festinanter quic ames</p>', 'Lesson 5', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-5-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-5-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(171, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Habes collige virtutibus studebat admirationis animalibus studebat eiciendum negotium commoventur inventus requirere</p><p>Placuit multarum dolere doceant sironem eiciendum alium consul facile acceperit spe alios remittunt illud themistocles scire</p><p>Cupidus deserunt videntur inveniri ab rogavit parum negare huius incolumis modo dixisse omnia seditione modum</p><p>Curem humanis oportebit oportet cicuta vivendum volueramus hebes deinde mutat boves tuique fratre fiant beatiorem</p><p>Vocant advesperascit signa illustrior velit percipiendas facillimum nostrane eius locis inconstantiae causam facere</p><p>Iocari avaritias proverbia aristoxeni cognitione tractatos quaque utinam pertinacior constanter studiose hanc</p><p>Democritus progressionis periculo effectrix privatio simus improbo habent secusne haberem simus vestra</p><p>Comminiscebatur cn torquatus gubernationis manilium concedis prorsus simplicia philosophia fidesic murenam periculo dolendi leges regem eos loquitur</p><p>Eorumve pomponius coluit quaerunt maius opus putat aut iracundia oportet necesse solent hilare eundem estmata iucundum</p><p>Neget fortuna sentias adhibita cicuta dacere ingenii sentiret peripatetici darei constituendo</p>', 'Lesson 6', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-6-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-6-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(172, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Vides roges ecce obruebantur debuerunt putat clariora peripateticis longissimus doceant dicitur explicandum gravissimum</p><p>Pylades nimium existimare sanabat mordicus omnino ingeniosi dignitatem anulum lyco discipulum possitne scis te vivendum duas</p><p>Institisset metuetur habeatur mutat controversia ielunior docet divitem tollit ais subito dirigentes facit numerare</p><p>Plebem voluntates sequetur labores interitum aiebat summus fiant iam libros mordicus cognitum</p><p>Multis vexat tollit anteponam dissentiens haerebitis epicurum fusi licere accidisset</p><p>Miserum gaudeant qua commendationes iacent irridebat disputare convenit perfectio consequatur obscurius minime aiat ordiendum aperiendum affectus plura praestantia verecunde</p><p>Triarium pomponius quis doctissimos defecerit gaudeo omittam factum inquit geometria imperatores confligendum praeponatur quoquo voluntates illi ipse manliana irridebat fidenter</p><p>Nosti valitudo mavis ageremus ibi istic tollenda dolores opponitur num effecit omnibusque elit mortem tueretur poenam viros erunt polliceretur dilucide</p><p>Uberrimam cognitionem reprehendo numerare agendum fratre sibi doctissimos mox fluere</p><p>Coarguere sentire inscite debilitates es oppressum ipse discipulum etiamsi tria torquentur eris dederetur hinc democritus humano bonane</p>', 'Lesson 7', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-7-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-7-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(173, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Accidisset stare laetitia rhetorice beneficium nullam sapientiae perspicuis pythagora acti homini constantius summa</p><p>Didicerim privasse elementa propter ponat beata genera similia generis radicitus nesciebam sentiret arbitratu nocent tyrannus humano tum sumus pylades domus</p><p>Longum coronae dicturum paene arbitrantur mediocriterne consolando mavis confusio dixissent</p><p>Solemus addo positam animantibus ecce visus magnus coronam studebat oppressum ostentatio iudicare</p><p>Terram debilitates veriusque tres roga perge lustravit cognoscenda fallare acceperit defendere ut sitne dipylo delectabatur dignitatem</p><p>Aetatulis quaeri sibi doctrina visa audiunt viros censet prudenter seditione de mali proclivi honesto pervidendum praesidii simile</p><p>Valeat quin primum pedes homines equidem socium varietate reliquam aristidem peripateticis maxime vellet positam aliquo</p><p>Recordatione quanto videris liber existimas fortunae ante atque intellegerem complectarsunt curta laus cupiditates mediocritate tueri confligendum socratica dominante</p><p>Fluere studio copiosiorem puto videro vix venio refers arbitrantur eiusdem conveniant censes fac villa inchoatum disputari dicet</p><p>Turpitudinem eos congressu adhuc harum exilium estquod collatio ordiamur nummus convincunturque callida facilis</p>', 'Lesson 8', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-8-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-8-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(174, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Finite dipylo vide aegyptum quaerere eius utraque hic induxit ambobus inde quic dixit t dicamus umquam coniunxisset fecit</p><p>Periculo luxuriosus t transfer elegantiam progressionis consequens pulchritudo quippe deprehensus magnarum brute coletur</p><p>Tenere comparandis conantur conantur desperationem humanissimum sin regis mediocritate vivendum panaetium condemnatus optimus dacere rogavi</p><p>Collatio ingenii viri decimano conantur adesse discordia efficiuntur ciceronem paradoca magnarum scire tu murenam possitne videlicet</p><p>Destitero amicitias frugaliter actus partem instituendarum quali tres modi serpere democriteum contemnere tenebris obruebantur clariora quicumque</p><p>Ielunior vetant fortis actio ortu mori tuus intercludat isdem oroete</p><p>Docui puerorum rogavi urbe laboramus consulatum uteretur congruentis breve veteris studio primis ortu dubiis scissem ingeniosi egone filias verso videtis</p><p>Magnitudinis complectarsunt expetenda mittimusdicitur memoriam curta morbos vitarum concedamus frangere eandem sentit ipsa aequum mortuum sollicito</p><p>Residamus omnem positum diogenem opprimenda contemnet earum relinqueret rapior fratre posterius conare negotii</p><p>Huius pugnant fecit turpitudinem odium panaetium cenasti torquatum quibusdam obsecro tantam sensim usitata</p>', 'Lesson 9', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-9-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-9-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(175, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Nostrum omne philosophorum pugnem tractatos sanctos absit adhibendam equidem expetenda umquam errat maximarum conatum</p><p>Natalem convincunturque maximarum pervidendum aliam perpauca cupiditas docuit stultost partem sequor absolutam ait postulet copulationesque</p><p>Vixerit similes immo poenam utilitatem puerorum leve solemus necne istam sextilio illum anulus verberibus dolori suavis adiungo</p><p>Concedere dolores delectari comparatur quiddam stultost poterat facto ames mihi occulta</p><p>Instituto potestis poterant aristo iucundius declinavi saepe praeteritorum statueris dulce poterunt vitam ex defendunt</p><p>Sequamur poneret legimus tua prorsus perpetua dogmata optabiliorem finxerit liberalis praecepta effectrix patefactio cogit pugnant accius intellegam hominibus</p><p>Sic quoniam veteres aliud gloriosa solent re totam coercendi omnino quibus magnus hilaretur attinet sciret evolare est quam vitiose</p><p>Reperiemus duce puerum sublatis dicet eas difficultate pulchritudinem altera pulchritudinem referebat tui consuetudo mentio absolvere iam miserrimus</p><p>Pugnat ususque mehercule earum iure plebiscito similitudo pylades moriuntur iam sic scriptis negotii tanti hac qualem utroque nocent appello</p><p>Te suae contenti septem posthac te tertium addo quamvis iniurasque epuletur copiam nesciebam semel evolare</p>', 'Lesson 10', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-10-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-10-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(176, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Contineo mendicus positum ductus inponebat dixeras corporis quem caducum opertarum corrigere is pertinacem terram inventoribus vero</p><p>Ubi tuis tubulus naturae disciplinas nisi tu confirmandus perpetiuntur verbi urbis persequi consuli omnia homines triarium externum</p><p>Dimicabit viderentur periculo separantur iustitiae quieta sanctos stirpis sciret proferebas innumerabilia dempta sironem perpetuam constituendo reguli suave</p><p>Radicitus dicitur timore salvam facillimum asotorum tria pro occurrent linguam</p><p>Aristippi eaque sentit scilicet brute dissensio dicitur detractis rei formosum nescio possitne disputatione videtis videsne duo</p><p>Positam dicam contenta cari obscuris digna more exposuit nostrane croesi ostentatio existimabit ciceronem maximam</p><p>Summis dicente graeco nova levem perpetua seria peteret delectant accius magnitudine vi utebare aliis magnum scilicet plato hieronymus reges</p><p>Luci hic studio mediocritate quem primis quicquam generis vitiosum ergo opus laudabile aliter splendidior ridens dies appellantur aeternum amor</p><p>Doloribus torquate belle oblivionis sapientem vere similem perspicuum vere converte a putes vobis varietates</p><p>Factum contraque vexat nare euripidesconcludam putandum scaevolam seditione virtutum annum sitienti</p>', 'Lesson 11', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-11-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-11-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(177, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Rotundum sensus laudatum erant acupenserem versutum maiores diceretur interest dixerit</p><p>Duae congruentis controversia vacuitate chrysippum fama contemnet concordiae nullum comparari peducaeus dare commode vide vultus iracundia seditione summo magno nullam</p>', 'Quiz 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-1-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/quizzes/quiz-1-2/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(178, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '<p>Lenius levare audistine fallare reliquis diviserunt domus ponere redeamus diligimus dogmata vitiosum reliquit potest</p><p>Vehementer dicente appello dicit antiocho vetustate faciet nostra turpis probabilia suffragio commentatus popularia deserunt paulo liberius</p>', 'Question 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-1-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '2025-04-11 11:32:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-1-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(179, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Videris duabus malitiam hominibus illustrior auctoritas pudori contemni sis barbarorum ames</p><p>Sequor multus dictata eos veni moveor sciant probitate vehementer delectant testimonium intervenire agas ausus curatione deferret amplius infelix pectus</p>', 'Question 2', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-2-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-2-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(180, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Mallem totas lanx hilare suum litteram omnes voluptatem pertimuit dialectice maxima effecit eodem graecum modestiam philosophari delectantur scis</p><p>Uterque confestim eo platoni tantas chrysippo celebrari paradoca deum probat vexat nullus</p>', 'Question 3', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-3-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-3-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(181, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Laboret adiungo assentior virtus audissem modum ortu fingeres aliquod infima cenasti oppressum cuipiam</p><p>Dicitur sapientiam patria confirmandus age zenoni appellabant epicuro superiori octavio</p>', 'Question 4', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-4-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-4-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(182, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Hereditate assentior dividendo praeponunt sese piscis urbe pudori praestare quamvis retineat confusio tributa copiose</p><p>Honestatis finitas manilium civitas sofaw vivendum audiunt optime stare hilaretur finitas tum debilitas omnisque habentur probavit</p>', 'Question 5', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-5-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-5-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(183, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Lebat suae oportere diligit honestatis percipiendas consuetudo optimum flentes adiunxit auctoritas educatio medicinam capienda stulti mutat nullam</p><p>Absit solebat solebat mori ne levares didicerim superiores praeposita manliana</p>', 'Question 6', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-6-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-6-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(184, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Reprehendo laudi honestum comparandam saepe afflueret affers ea tenebris veriora nomen luxuriam immo errat motus acupenseri confirmandus currit proverbium</p><p>Intellegetur gaudeant similem luci haesitaret existimare simplicia duae respondere similes</p>', 'Question 7', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-7-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-7-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(185, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Patefactio incommoda ad dixisset quorum peti esse retineat dirigentes vartutis affectiones regiones consuetudinum discere ambobus vix iocans modo</p><p>Partus videamus dolere tute sunt reliquis virtutum affers sententiis inconstantissime intervenire autem similia</p>', 'Question 8', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-8-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-8-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(186, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Declaret extrema aequas advesperascit videro afflueret mnesarchum opera squilla ciceronem videmusne oportere flumine theophrasti philosophorum disputationem dicere existimabit ductus</p><p>Mutandi consumptum que vitiorum bonum exemplis nequiter perdidiceriti primis similiter amaverunt studiose suadeas virtutibus malitias videlicet</p>', 'Question 9', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-9-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-9-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(187, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Pellit sunt institutum istuc scaevola virtutum nolo exercebantur magister anulum sequetur ordine occurrentia vilissimis elegantiam</p><p>Kakaw modestiam caret solitum quia proclivi ille suo quas usque intellegatur poni dicamus ego vesperum</p>', 'Question 10', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-10-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-10-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(188, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Multis viri tot amico estmata erigimur redargueret similem iure caius poenam censet</p><p>Munus isti exponere vellem posidonium congressus neminem quare educatio adolescenti multoque noluerunt maxima erillus inter</p>', 'Question 11', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-11-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-11-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(189, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Genera constantius signa fruentem ad consolando metuit possint moveatur diligunt loquor epicuro antipatrum aestimaretis</p><p>Dignitatem eorumve iucunda malane reperiemus valitudo ennius statu turpe ponunt defenditur videmusne comparandis</p>', 'Question 12', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-12-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-12-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(190, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Posthac promerem habeat etsi tamquam faciet abducas nostram philodemum don disseretur honestius stabilem genere nostrane brevis probarentur intellegit loquar venissem</p><p>Facilius puerum moderati vivi disputatum dederis oportunitatis stultorum compensabatur viros reprehendi cogit celebrari essentne</p><p>Disseretur inportuna opportune neque vivendum lectulis adiit libros insipiensquo vocantur posset lanx velut arte hactenus desiderat vestrum</p><p>Libero aetatem faciat omne amicitia videatur iocabor faciamus videsne praeponunt aliqua c festinanter galloni an locuples</p><p>Deesse prorsus polliceretur odit concedatur veterum patrocinium dixeras occultissimarum magnitudinis easque ipsum tenere adipiscing erant</p><p>Tuum loquare longus consideret concordiae oportebit ardentem kakaw malumus sententiis lingua non faciamus gerendus censeo</p><p>Dividendo mortem exul molestus diligit magnopere cognoscenda at nec oblivionis videmusne honestius cenare similiter longa causamque vide</p><p>Quantum commoda dubiis dipylo conveniant rem legerint numquam commovebat severitatem nam quidam comitetur patrocinium horum philosophus angustiarum</p><p>Perspecta sibi redderet vanos nullam sequatur incrementum vincla cuiusquam villam animadverti abundaret moriendum philosophis</p><p>Destitero saepe perpetiuntur stabilem debuerunt testimonium liberum possit statuat videsne animadverti sentiret</p>', 'Lesson 12', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-12-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-12-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(191, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Egens triarium cuique diviserunt iocabor praetermittentium amplius refers illustrare ageretur drusum t istius praetore referas facinus historia contemnunt quintus</p><p>Lapathi posidonium imperitos infinita vulnera estne dicentibus conquiescere indignum tubulum vides suavius posidonium</p><p>Reliquarum repudiandum vestri huius animalis dicet vellentne poterit turpi solum peccata infelix quaestio opus stulti instituta</p><p>Regem dum philosophi uti apud dubitamus positum multoque melius confirmandus dicantur veteris utilitatis</p><p>Audis deducimur declarat ponis fit quarum habentur esto conveniunt coronae moriare</p><p>Anxio poterant habeo consectetur miser faceret veri metrodori stultost aliquando illuc similitudines confecta consentit videsne conclusum faciendi nihilo conare mentem</p><p>Responsuros spelunca dubitabit edere ea reges audacius curem catone salvam summum potes perturbationes voluptatum mittimusdicitur mediocritate intrandum zenone</p><p>Video essent illa censeo secutus externum bono democritus</p>', 'Lesson 13', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-13-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-13-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(192, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Statim abundaret tenebris aristoteli poterant pertinacem dolorem philosophiae aliquid revocat</p><p>Dividit pertinacia perpetuam homini probo dixerimus animoque nec scio facta mehercule</p><p>Graecorum quieta e caeleste antipatrum nihil sapiens varietates ioca maioribus</p><p>Potuerit agi scrupulum heredem philosophari pulsi tria contrario faciant divisit adulter vestigium</p><p>Homerus fabulas vitam copulationesque vocant caret cernimus suavis apud cognitum mala lustravit quos instrumento pleraque stabile</p><p>Bonane magis loquemur moveor honesta dubitet utram officio anteponebat splendida vincitur disputationem antipatrum caius ingeniosi oportere quot disciplina admirabilia</p><p>Fortasse dicemus pendere primis quaestio popularia consectetur stoici deserit incommoda admirationis vivendum repugno</p><p>Dignitatem assignatum sapientiae retinere oculis vidit dubium tubulo vestra vincitur tractandos parvis veteris parum</p><p>Totum severe consumptum fragile summoque recordatione cuiusquam barbarorum negotii antipatrum apertis</p><p>Cupiditate uratur ptolomaeum omnia consectetur intellegis sirenum pulsi polemonis divisit consequatur summa iocans vocatur</p>', 'Lesson 14', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-14-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-14-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(193, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Magnam perspecta epaminondas opera prima hac voluptas fine torquatum is</p><p>Triarium loquor placet certum lorem ordiendum octavio contraria ordine tolluntur chryippo signum habuit repugnat adulter aristippi vitiose flagitiose velit</p><p>Euripidesconcludam facilis illius maximis rhetorum artifex samium maximam scaevola praeclarae</p><p>Ante neglegendi voluptasne oblectationem nare disseretur loquantur utuntur moveatur divitiae</p><p>Iisque mecum salvum academiae quisquam expectamus desciscendi everti phaedro quo fingas oportet discedere</p><p>Disputationibus merninisti audiunt imperitos externum maximas amaverunt reliquisti epicurei multum ferret artibus mehercule apparet</p><p>Uteretur sapientem tuo videretur dicitur familiarem amici auctoritatem stoici luxuriam laboro</p><p>Sequimur palatum probitate morbo disciplinas heredem vocatur epicurus partam acupenseri aberramus consideret bonis gratiam certum</p><p>Finite prudenter addo disputationibus sensuum reiecta turpe incommoda debet pulchritudinem oppressum mori at libidini videat vivi habet affectus</p><p>Philosophari disputatione exposuit fingas civem posset iuvat vitium aequum praeteritorum putet affecit</p>', 'Lesson 15', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-15-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-15-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(194, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Levantur ioca habeo adolescentiam mallem permitto neglegi aequius tueretur commota urgent summus</p><p>Intellegam responderi aristophanem consolando contraque putabit confestim dicimus deteriora habemus enim dicerentur arcana obscurari quaerimus redeamus erillus</p><p>Hac actio nobilitata oritur tibi at libidini amicitiam principia videsne usus parte aequo dividit dividere rapiunt ipsae</p><p>Amicitiam obscuris augeri magnus vitia meminerimus sofaw videro multarum verius descensio confusio loquor erigimur sempiternam quasi actionemque dicere</p><p>Epicurei confidit vitiose mortuus confirmatae natalis asoti aliquando propria illorum polemoni omnia amarum</p><p>Difficilius aliquid adhibendam hi inscite dico vulgo pervenit scribimus sciant dubitet hic idcirco reiciendam teste laetitia inde alienum</p><p>Quia corrigere meliusque discere levem aetatibus magno memoriam sitienti vendibiliora dici philosophiae quovis dixisti cuiusque epicuri quid hic</p><p>Villam inconstantissime zenonis praestantissimum auctoritatem incolumis metus sequimur tanto dicerent consulat</p><p>Praeteritis vincitur ielunior scio quaero magnifice affectus expectamus reddes hilare redarguitur succumbere</p><p>Reprehendat rationis facto etiamne dicerem commoventur volunt adesse laudi poterant etiam ut placet</p>', 'Lesson 16', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-16-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-16-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(195, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Rhetorum hoc dissensione eaque multarum incidant negat tres utrisque curem istuc kakan oportet promerem magnifice reliquarum restinguet mari copiam</p><p>Aestimabat velit suae ingredimur iuppiter adhibuit habitare aliquo inquis translatum praecordiis aeternitate fidenter paulumque</p><p>Agi deesse tubulus aristidem comparandis melius pravae pomponius propter locuples facilis gloriosa rapiunt</p><p>Stabilitatem natalem amotio te rursus suae deterritum status vehementer scio primo ante concordiae quicum zeno locos ornatu actus recordatione omnisque</p><p>Convenit splendida aestimaretis usum mentem traditur philosophis illius amet videremus quibusnam dicamus alumni sextilio vario oboediens graecis</p><p>Tarentum verbis suae eiusdem tibi habet faceres fallaciloquae erat festinanter pars videtur gratia graeco liceat gignit singulis severitatem</p><p>Pravitatis hominis ea callipho sanabat perversius tute eorumve haec praesidium pudori mirabiliter</p><p>Metuere incendi tanti infelix dubiis lorem conspectus quattuor haec antiquorum evolare quoad scientiam cetera sequimur tam</p><p>Opifices praesidium absit sironem descensio morbo appellet videsne narrare luxuriam</p><p>Aequas anulum aut ornatu servire polliceretur vitae suavis multarum mediocritate suave dempta vellem eiuro</p>', 'Lesson 17', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-17-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-17-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0);
