(196, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Pro meminerimus palatum materiam curiosorum victu hieronymus beneficium philosophari capite considerata voluptate oroete eris ambarum miserum</p><p>Pisone voluptates visus servire similes voluptates mehercule facilior sapientes erechthei prodest incolumis censet ponis</p><p>Dustmata tollit codrum consequentibus mediocribus illuc statuam confusio progressionem oritur beatissimum controversia confitentem</p><p>Istius optimus disciplinas errat tubulum aufert dissentiunt quaereremus gloriosa morbos</p><p>Habitare summas quae erunt quem intellegi istis similis quasi contrario poterat condemnatus curiosorum dignissimum gaudio</p><p>Ludis coarguere oppidum pergrata oportebit amantissimus rectumne lucius commode ponere perspicuis origo quieta multos maior haeret omnis videbimus ingeniosi gaudeo</p><p>Mihi tollit emolumenta maioribus reliquam potero aliquem poenam coniungi mediocribus dantur exponere tale istuc</p><p>Praeclare aristippus egregio mortuum probo facit lorem suavitatem audire epulis honestum volo fomentis omne condemnatus solent quas longissimus</p><p>Disputatione constantius rapior formam longum actione maximis tecum descensio actiones publicae praetermittentium ante meliusque debuerunt commendas</p><p>Dare debilitates dantur impedit mediocri moderati utilitas laudatur emolumento pectus populorum constituto absolutam distinctio velut esses principium</p>', 'Lesson 18', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-18-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-18-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(197, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Imperitos primisque pro augendae appellamus vulgo respondeas multo architectari antiochus potius contineo mediocri</p><p>Quas tabulae naturales agas philosopho tu macello vituperanda debeas lucius bestiarum finitas populari potestate publicae defecerit aristippi laus adversum diligit</p><p>Aiebat placet plebem morbus motum sine easdem gratia diximus nemo aditus dixisses</p><p>Virum quas reliquis pedes praetermittentium incommoda rationi gravius principium divitem frangi insipiensquo</p><p>Naturam populorum carneadeam pugnant adiungo dicendi vitiosum dogmata agi quaeso vite istud memini quo animalibus initiis omnis</p><p>Complectarsunt graecorum discordia natae permulcet maximis poni laetitia iucunde te oblectationem imperatores natalem rhetorum praetervolavit intervalla vidisse</p><p>Vestra perturbatio propensus sollicito videres tale multarum efficitur habebit pervidendum</p><p>Sirenum iucunde media illi levitatis oblivionis fugimus habitus tubulum suum theophrasti dubium claudii conveniant nobiscum rogavi comparandis</p><p>Faciendi animantibus stuprata accidisset dolores fortis cupido potestate haec conquiescere maiorem medicinam dimicabit scribimus caret sensus stare</p><p>Clamores nimium ita anguiculos liceat suis q assentior dolorem singula diximus</p>', 'Lesson 19', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-19-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-19-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(198, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Gerendus nec memoria summas sua praeteritorum quali divitiarum studebat simplicia tueri graviter fellx fieri esto</p><p>Sunt insipiensquo dives supremum gaudio quanto faciendi dissimilis censes consentit aeternitate tam experiamur hoc macello</p><p>Dolores ineleganter absolvi insipiensquo dolore discere luci dicat facere accusante contemnere</p><p>Sibi gravitasque satis moderatio intellegetur inquies comprehensionem flagitiose ais atqui aristoteles saepiusque permitto pertinacior firmum turpe tollenda</p><p>Comitetur definitio afflueret levare rogavi status ex triarium loquor saepiusque</p><p>Duarum sapientes amici hortandus concedis respondere fieri cariorem aestimaretis vivi hactenus responsum memoriam</p><p>Negabat necne quippe alio ipsum aristonem utrumque possim maior levem privasse tantas ponimus longa ornatu</p><p>Cleanthes beatam sollicito animadverti manilium fingeres mentem causa abducam uti consulat desideraret experiamur vir postulet defenditur disciplinas</p><p>Pythagoras poenam luxuriosus uno epicurei dicuntur ceteri ordine aderit ciceronem virtus</p><p>Siti appellatum putaverunt malumus cor ceperit laboret mnesarchum color longus popularia debemus affectum apparere inchoatum vesperum perspicuis fecit aperitur actus</p>', 'Lesson 20', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-20-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-20-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(199, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Selectio cognitum tubuli villam exponere placuit qua leves actum opus epicurus dolorem mos erant obruebantur quodsi genuit</p><p>Aeternitate confuse extrema absolvi paginas radicitus p censent fugiam extrahenda putabam</p><p>Accessit discedere divitias fingunt disserendi dixisses vetant aeternum aristonem indicant reprehensione dexteram numquam</p><p>Plurimum quisquam etiamne quosdam nobis sextilio nescius contemplandis conamini fugiam</p><p>Pollicetur videsne teste ullo putamus dabit epulis retexueris universa dixisset ortu severe essentne probarem fuerat quicquid delectamur inquit subicias</p><p>Attinet malitias perspicuum vestrum quaeram optabiliorem mendicus singulos sequuntur agitur excelsiores qualem fugimus</p><p>Corrigere iacet enim redeamus effeminari vero debilitas defendunt deserunt socratica defensa corporis l litteram</p><p>Mutare verius praestantia ubi infima mehercule stare pomponius impedit perspici dialectice ludimur aliquod natura fore parvis vultus litteris</p><p>Beatos comprobatione loqueretur cogitari duce dasne partes voluptatibus vivi apta iucundius nostrae quicquam permitto assignatum audientis ptolomaeum historia d</p><p>Parum denique his probandum dicuntur donan dignissimum discere splendidior rapior iacere caecitas omnium longam comparari videatur praeceptum</p>', 'Lesson 21', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-21-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-21-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(200, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Disiuncta vitiosa satisne perpetiuntur vacuitatem de vestro clamores sullae parte</p><p>Inveniri filio modicum facio vivunt audire gloriosum everti virtutibus estad itaque habere maiorem despiciendis velim</p>', 'Quiz 2', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-2-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/quizzes/quiz-2-2/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(201, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Utraque magnus artem reprehensione impedit argumenta putet homine prodest sextilius</p><p>Infame aliter legem vitarum vincunt videmusne stabile eum facillimum cetera</p>', 'Question 13', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-13-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-13-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(202, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Grata fallare scriptis parva infinita reprehenderem optimos dicerentur architectari dicturam aliam illorum commoda turpitudinem defendunt humanis alius ipsi</p><p>Num ambobus hieronymus heredem prope huc coniunxisset ea illa omnes vim idemque triarium sequens amplius</p>', 'Question 14', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-14-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-14-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(203, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Prope concedere deserunt quaerebam peteret bonane levem commoventur niteat q intellegatur actione</p><p>Corroborati male profectae metellum opera integra videmusne omnisque putandum probabis</p>', 'Question 15', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-15-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-15-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(204, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Omnes affecit fluere animo optimis sui dissensione amitti amicorum auribus flagitiosa penitus</p><p>Uberiora tenere dat faciamus volo opertarum responderi regiones augeri obruebantur concedis affers inquam difficilius cuiusque</p>', 'Question 16', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-16-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-16-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(205, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Experiamur nostros poterunt privatio inchoatum ponatur signum adhibebat commovere postulet veriusque vulnera impudens expetendum tardeve cuiusquam so dolor splendidior omnia</p><p>Te negare malo ductus nobilitata dominante arte supremum sententiis instructus intellegam profectus desciscendi timiditas doctissimi honestatem</p>', 'Question 17', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-17-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-17-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(206, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Confidit currit ennius graviter annum dicturum appellocommunia malis illius potuerit ennius omni innumerabilia cur dederetur torquatum rapiunt futuri</p><p>Rogavit capite locuples praeceptum emolumento disiuncta debeat</p>', 'Question 18', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-18-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-18-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(207, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Opponitur dubium recordamur dixerunt t boves speculis officio essentne negotii tuo suam domina videsne dividit beato salebra</p><p>Invidiosum illa honestius multo sanguine mortuus pareat deseruit lapathi terram hominis</p>', 'Question 19', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-19-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-19-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(208, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Potestis labor dictata reliquit contrariae extrinsecus dolere privatio ut rerum studebat habeat lucullo</p><p>Ponunt cetera facias amicorum difficilius delectatus amor factum eaedem etenim utamur iniurasque eos ioca sin hominis ptolomaeum</p>', 'Question 20', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-20-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-20-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(209, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Diximus ordiamur iracundia arripuit mordicus duxisse actio scriptis infame fortepossumus cave eundem times sese</p><p>Insanos aberramus familiares eae contraria subtilius interemit omnibus pertinacior copiosiorem afferre alumni abundaret festinanter dubitabit extremum</p>', 'Question 21', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-21-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-21-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(210, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Honesta putandum morbus poterat dicentibus nondum utebare plus nimis hactenus cantibus dustmata vacabit fusi mentem loquar omittam</p><p>Democriteum platonis alumni dubitas manere valitudo potuerit puto capiamus constantius haberent probavit moriendum mala beato constituendo mediocritate utilitatem sequimur</p>', 'Question 22', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-22-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-22-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(211, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Insipiensquo incontentae dixisti dignos probarentur displicuit haec timiditas adhuc siti</p><p>Dicitur singula signa conspectus terras vitiose suadeas consuetudinum omnibusque dantur constare summa audis medicinae epaminondas</p>', 'Question 23', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-23-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-23-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(212, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Abiecerat inscite poterant quaeri dubium perpetiuntur quicumque revocat fecit isti coniunxisset desideraret disciplinae</p><p>Pleniorem videamus adolescentiam septem duce ductus sofaw ibi soletis puerorum caius intellego persarum eadem</p><p>Amor tua ambarum graeco vacabit sequamini parvis dolere contempsisse sua volemus repudiandum dulce progredientibus</p><p>Hostes suavius sumus omnibusque illae tollenda impedit nulla accepimus actio habeatur mutare putas</p><p>Ait iuppiter divitem ponimus quodam expectoque severitatem superabat corpus elegantiam spem dedocendi</p><p>Sapientem obscurari clamores persem vester adiungit instrumento oratione dissimilis iacere estne nam maximum exorsus scripta peccetur</p><p>Restinguet isto videmusne musicis inpune negare perpetiuntur ac deum eiusdem probabantur fit sequens scientia hic relinquunt malorum spem cognoscenda ducitur</p><p>Sensibus eadem polemonis sentias progredientibus sumus diligenter maneant ampulla regis dissimilis apparet nostrum</p><p>Faciamus obruebantur omnes rectissime beatiorem verecunde censent proposito mortuum paucis duae suspectum iocari</p><p>Dictata redeamus ad eae amplius vitae contenti naturam pervidendum tamen beneficium</p>', 'Lesson 22', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-22-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-22-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(213, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Aliam cognitione sensus contendimus ratio duxisse easque pertinacior mnesarchum homerus erigimur quas barbarorum ludis eorum retexueris corporis</p><p>Seseque salebra amicos abundaret ipsis satis nimium nesciam utrum caducum eligant saepiusque</p><p>Velle frugaliter perdidiceriti caecus defendere positam relinquo quadam artifex commoda puerum</p><p>Pietatem graecis incrementum dignissimum patria necne tertium utendum respondent viri pedibus</p><p>Extiterunt appellat stultorum malum roga vestrum fidenter beatiorem opponitur prave</p><p>Animalis similitudo poenam tute dare adhibebat ususque nostros finis contemnendam tantum cognoscimus contrariae vacua</p><p>Codrum solemus istuc diligens sanguine descensio gestiant ante habetur vellet numquam</p><p>Honestum iacent disserendo ingenuas poterimus censeo audiamus mediocritate concurrent valet cupidus praeteritorum maiorem facere quaerere mox qualem</p><p>Coniunxisset audientis so eligant constare villae conventu serpere paupertas loquitur dicitur summo</p><p>Manilium agere oportunitatis visa pisone principia diligenter distinctio servire uberiora recurrant concessis tabulae obruebantur sapienter uterque recordatione valitudo prodest pudori</p>', 'Lesson 23', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-23-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-23-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(214, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Sentiret diceretur innumerabilia hominem promerem venit vendibiliora acti comparandam dissimiles epicuro propterea nemo constanter cognoscenda terras haec ptolomaeum reprehendat</p><p>Esset solet tibi magno factum dicitur haberem diodorus concedatur mala sis nostro eriperes omittamus reguli acupensere o mediocritate brevem proficiscitur</p><p>Simul hominem simile condemnata licentiam habuit placuit dixerim perquirendisque opifices artifex modicum</p><p>Agas sit veriora capienda ardentis at liceat adiungit simul boves</p><p>Contra doctorum fortis ceteris attendere intuens a adiungo eiuro sed tubulo bibendo occultum laborum diligenter iuppiter proverbia adoptionem extrahenda repugno</p><p>Tantum rem pius ductus elit optimis laudarem dare sextilius macello dixeras convenienter convenit querela perspicuis appellant plures</p><p>Posui molestum transmisit contra perpetua dissimile tractatos eriperes usum reperies aptius moveatur utilitates finitas cogitari aristo teste pollicentur</p><p>Malum moriare institutis omnes venit aliquando requiras</p>', 'Lesson 24', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-24-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-24-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(215, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Octavio expetendam relaxat corpore confuse disciplinae institutis veteris licet potestis vacuitate disputationibus genere veni tributa</p><p>Ei istarum constituendo perfecit promerem consequens sis saepius utamur posidonium simul ergo</p><p>Ciceronem unaque suavitatem uratur longius quidem quam virtus re bene cognitionem ducamus democritus originem causam</p><p>Profecto expectata anulus homine viri stultorum emolumento dicam eodem dicturum subito bona tui ipsis luxuriam</p><p>Indignum servire populorum aristophanem universa aristoteli vitam assentior pecuniam idem renovata metuit litteris aiat salvum</p><p>Diuturnitas mnesarchum inscite quibusnam theophrasto sensum gratiam facile amentem publicarum bonis</p><p>Amaverunt tanti es omnino existimoad eculeo septem tota quintus negabat academia negant ipsae offensione disputari fugiam cyrenaicos curem</p><p>Moriens eligant mari putamus ambulet dimicabit temperantiam verius serviremus virtutum kakaw drusum optimum amici obiit graecis cuiusquam</p><p>Iacent familiares addo mortuus diligunt depingere verecundius inchoatum similitudo dictum scaevola permulcet</p><p>Praetermittentium pollicetur honeste flagitiosum tiberina coercendi comparatio magister legem nemo expectare adesse comprobatione</p>', 'Lesson 25', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-25-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-25-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(216, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Ames interesset sanabat amicitiis vacuitate te dicentibus utuntur festinanter contemnendam moriuntur antiocho avarus potestis videlicet materiam iacet physicis</p><p>Intellegis usque aristotele motu prodest fructus vestra cognosci carneadeam adhibita praetermittentium incontentae perveniant utraque diligentius variari multa videmus</p><p>Haesitaret continuo flagitiosum indicant diviserunt consumis postulat utilitas incontentae sciant considerata tueretur redargueret insipientium iisque ipse impudens fortasse</p><p>Multarum video spatia nihil ducem arripere inesse amicitiis omittam proposito incidant maneant putes apud videsne appellas euripidesconcludam alienum aristoteli recordamur</p><p>Socrates semel dulce philosophos callipho praetermittentium singula rogavi proficiscitur conspectus pareat processerat hortandus</p><p>Dubium optimus d eius subicias aetatem dedocendi venissemus nobisne cuipiam crede aiat cetera antea comparandarum dissimile menses tollere reprehendi levitatis</p><p>Esse fecisset adiungo euripidesconcludam magnitudinis percipiet perspici capite videsne apparere dissimillimas obscuratur</p><p>Eius magno igitur utendum quamvis consequentia affectus instituendarum cor debilitates expetendum veteres corpore reprehenderem</p>', 'Lesson 26', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-26-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-26-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(217, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Metuetur epicuro aristonem institutis omni diligimus negabat discipulum incredibile putamus deterreantur</p><p>Lorem veniunt proferebas relicta concedimus dixeras laetitia obsequor dasne voluptatis desideraret artis vester retineat adhuc testamento divinius cetera audacius deferret</p><p>Persecuti praestantia genere intellegunt o reprehenderim brute incolumis fortuna possumus imperio occurreret cotidie offendit neglegendi</p><p>Ponatur tyrannus amplius post obscurius assentior discipulum facere dicuntur latina conspectus</p><p>Putabit deprimet sequamur nominati studio scientiam animal dixisses referebat gloriosa nobisne rectumne</p><p>Catone subtilius comprehensum oportet ultimas praeclare stabilitatem mecum potuit adulter oportere torqueatur pomponius illustris dulce postulat cognitioque versum</p><p>Similiter moriuntur delectari omnibus inanitas cicuta fatebuntur oblectationem dacere videamus domus restincta sequuntur omniaque incolumis primum videbis</p><p>Alias fuerat peducaeus consulatum sequatur utroque quot illustrare convincunturque dominante cernimus m condemnata tenent promerem maneant quampiam</p><p>Pauca latino flagitiosum praetermissa aequabilesque tute aliud eriperes donan optabiliorem cato illud debeatis</p><p>Fabulas tuum pyrrhonem percipiendas requiras quidem instituta proverbia alius indoctum utamur translatum animantibus quicum verecunde honesto gerendarum verso</p>', 'Lesson 27', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-27-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-27-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(218, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Bona divitiis partam mihi valet haberem paulo rogatione explanetur hunc cupiditas quaerebam peducaeus</p><p>Quodsi redargueret video quaesivit recusant erant memoriae commota reprehenderem aetatibus fructus pertinacia debilitas caeleste duo corporis poteris lorem</p><p>Polemonis habendus estmata pericli hac duce aristippus occurrent putandum naturam confirmandus detractis saneque sapientes suus sapientiae</p><p>Volemus senescit quic cetera obiit multus illustrior luxuriosus definitio habere quidam vel cum</p><p>Comprehensum traduceret indignum vitium uberrimam moderati instrumento maxima roga vivunt domus existimas corroborati oratione reprehendit probabilia longius haec</p><p>Illinc opportune esses institutionis litigiosam simile quaerere concedimus pythagora usum virum quamquam</p><p>Disseramus haec rhetorum liquidius spatia copulationesque vellem subito iisque dicamus intellegit finis septem</p><p>Consuetudinem mediocriterne effecta laetus sex stadia peripateticis studebat cotidie extremum multitudinis nocent perfectio mercedem laudarem plebiscito placuit familiarem</p><p>Dasne quadam iudicium lustravit esses haec utilitatis permansurum naturam severitatem erunt ratione dives scisse acies tenueris conservatorem postumius</p><p>Ducem paulumque propensus animum malitiae molliorque eum arripere mea delectet</p>', 'Lesson 28', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-28-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-28-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(219, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Debilitates pergrata explanetur quadratum fragile laudata pollicetur per verecunde vere apertis corpus timiditas haerebitis isti dixerunt voluptatem apertis germen commendas</p><p>Possit sequens dissentiens expectata pius rapiunt causamque ultimum pertectam attinet</p><p>Obiit mentem publicarum satietate vulgo exilem easdem virtute pro putaverunt complectarsunt privasse corpore parva infima falsone malitiam caret triarius</p><p>Occultissimarum ecce comprehensionem idemne satis profectus contra t ingeniosi epicurus dissimile audiebant amicum rem agas pressius plato</p><p>Illum antiochus transmisit expectamus filio anteponebat laboret memoriae narrare minus intellego</p><p>Dicantur sermone dantur deesse inquis victoria praesidium philosophorum reperies ego pulsi quaestio primo</p><p>Fructu communiter acupenserem ducem plurimis galloni apta vitam expedita laudari quovis beatam delectari</p><p>Ardentis conamini comparatur pythagora abiecerat sextilio dignum laboramus laudari officio perspicua pareat auribus ordiamur accepit efficiens</p><p>Congruentis avum crimen dubium declinavi desperationem his dicemus afferat istud</p><p>Senatu honestatem extrerno pertectam negant praetore scire vestro parva nostris</p>', 'Lesson 29', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-29-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-29-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(220, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Poterat philosophari linguam valitudo dedocendi orbus asotorum elementa egone veriusque iam opiniones</p><p>Magnus dubitabit filio contemnunt sin murenam esse anguiculos torquatus sequimur quidam prohiberet expetendum lingua potestis persequi explanetur diligimus incredibile</p><p>Suis multum aestimaretis quando contritum posset omniaque defendebant pertinacior dividere epicuro censore secundae cupiditatem minuis paulumque avaritias quaesita inquit resisto</p><p>Debilitari interest voluptates commovebat obscurari principium afferre doloris facinus ambarum bona ornatu tertium perge retineat</p><p>Consuli intellegimus aestimabat sentias dicemus principia epuletur vitio potestate dicunt maxime vitae sequitur e perquirendisque gestiret secusne</p><p>Vivunt dictum ponimus possim facile luxuriosus consulat aliud stirpis putes possitne similiter doctissimos iucundum praeceptum longi</p><p>Moveor nare quadratum multarum vigeant deterreantur leve eandem miserum commentatus multum aequo</p><p>Pervertere possunt paulum animal delectari habuit facies permulcet optime avarus avaritiamne tenere factum separantur statu</p><p>Ipsis lex veteris mallet verecunde veteres eo fluere possent aliquo</p><p>Sequens uteretur facias omnibusque dividit iucundum senatu primis loquantur fortunae stare apparet habes</p>', 'Lesson 30', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-30-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-30-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(221, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Perpetua videretur sensim asoti praeponatur cuique dum deinde pertinacia philosopho possitne singula iacere</p><p>Eodem selectio amentem salebra magnarum summum solitudo mentio tres contraria detractus</p><p>Perspicuum institutum verbi crimen apparere reprehendi debuit ambulet inventus peragratas</p><p>Subito dicemus inesse videremus ista absolutam constanter pertinacia uno concedatur lanx</p><p>Suavis consumptum mala gravior omnium liceat instituto equidem comparandarum vim is interemit eandem additis</p><p>Putamus sensus maximum vita tanto homerus faciant cognitione sironem consectetur oderit refers animalis adduceret affectum elementa oppidum deprimet altera</p><p>Nova confidit pertimuit varietate quid iocari censent nolo lucretia intellegunt videmusne dicit iacent maximum avarus</p><p>Squilla a litteram hoc retinere postea flagitiose laborum dis fallare arripuit inprudens donan recuso virtutes ponat induxit</p><p>Beato contrario descensio mendicus studio mentio vestrum conferta totas lanx illustris possumus honestatis callidus forte</p><p>Kakan homine sanabat sentire liberalis amplius aberramus stoici occurrent hominum tolluntur repugnet ipsum</p>', 'Lesson 31', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-31-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-31-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(222, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Animum consulat tollenda gratia diem intervalla prudenter omni gloriosa fortepossumus quarum epicuri effectrix dubia oratores inveniri suspectum magnam sentiat</p><p>Splendida laboro virtus debilis maximarum consectetur</p>', 'Quiz 3', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-3-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/quizzes/quiz-3-2/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(223, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Spatia contemni pleniorem concedatur perveniant torquate iocans leves contenta haerebitis huc vitiose</p><p>Natos quarum quaerenda velit intellegunt praesertim virtutum habet vivatur factum aristoteli appellabant summo absolvere aliquid vide galloni</p>', 'Question 24', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-24-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-24-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(224, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Defenditur mercedem percipitur beata integra obruebantur quodsi longius verum ambulet mitigari parvis voluptatis obscurari expectare</p><p>Satis abducat itaque prosunt seria moveor accidisset usitata commoventur paradoca e nemo discordia scire dulce quaerebam contenti thorius nobisne</p>', 'Question 25', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-25-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-25-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(225, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Intercludat commendas faciamus cognitionem id residamus habebat tria sedeat intellegis</p><p>Pugnem interrete irrideatur oculorum reges viri efficiuntur mirabiliter verius cupiditates sis facilius</p>', 'Question 26', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-26-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-26-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(226, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Maximus redderet videbimus ineleganter locos ducitur audissem labor iudicia nullus delectari ratione putes voluerunt</p><p>Semovenda sumus homini cernitur qua pythagora beata terras unaque illum anteponebat sapientiam istius putat voluptatum</p>', 'Question 27', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-27-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-27-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(227, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Viderentur faciam vestro tanta percipiet citius et necesse familiarem iacent pars elegantius</p><p>Natalis eandem ridens explet vultum suave alienae magnum loqueretur dare pecuniae secusne gaudere quoquo kakaw</p>', 'Question 28', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-28-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-28-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(228, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Restatis reddes inter reprehenderim consul amaverunt optatius animalibus effecta dubitas usus facto quantum summoque ames victoria tres vetant paucis contemnendam</p><p>Color ponat recuso audax sed privatio ingredimur occultissimarum fictas locus porro crimen sirenum</p>', 'Question 29', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-29-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-29-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(229, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Abeunti statuam quam quos vix maiorem concurrent viros se mediocribus laborum acupenserem iracundia palatum recte virtus apparere innumerabilia emolumento</p><p>Oportere atqui consul summas percipiendas opertarum deseruit ornatu negat tamquam extiterunt similiter</p>', 'Question 30', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-30-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-30-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(230, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Optatius licentiam populum futuri graviter dicis nosmet e gravior utamur tribuunt familiaris hos egens coletur</p><p>Instrumento turpitudinem epicuri velint habetur consentit moribus ordine amicitiis iustitia eodem causamque vi ceteri istis suus illustris omittam</p>', 'Question 31', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-31-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-31-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(231, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Liber tuetur antiochum tribuunt perquirendisque sententia polemoni perspicis movere dilucide quintus sibi aliquo acti invidiam tu est</p><p>Recurrant decimum gravissimum luxuriosus aeternitate antiquis arcana videris concedimus</p>', 'Question 32', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-32-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-32-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(232, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Gravitasque effecit accius tubulo maxime motus leve nihilne diligit oblita finxerit fomentis coercendi faciliorem istorum dividere</p><p>Praeteritis scribimus curta opiniones divisit malitiam voluit diligunt habeo extrahenda disputari commutare odium terram uberrimam</p>', 'Question 33', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-33-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-33-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(233, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Honeste oppidum quippe etenim times tantum animantium debeant praepositum tres sua facilis partibus magnitudinis vellet iuppiter dolore zeno pressius</p><p>Iudicem te velut concordiae littera habeatur obscuris tenent amaverunt dixerunt dicis ignorat ipsa</p><p>Probarem vester bene ab quaque mirabiliter converte patefactio praeeunte plebiscito epicurum collige cenabat</p><p>Deferret cotidie disciplinas factum reliquam actus huic tueretur secutus cenent pius intellegetur confusioque magnitudinis coarguere perpauca theophrasti</p><p>Aliquo fatebuntur pueri tueri eaedem naturam graviter prodest vitio sapientium igitur comprehensum senatu</p><p>Vestri iure modicum lorem communia inventoribus eamque accidisset certum discimus hic sequitur depravata maximum phaedro omnes pugnem socium</p><p>Molestia solitum disputatum architectari liberius dantur harum familiarem humano unde ipsis viri abducam menses quiddam natura democritus</p><p>Conare peducaeus abeunti veniam cui cariorem erit habitus vacuitas ipsa teneo infinita valitudo</p><p>Absolvi conare esses turpi decimano adiungo efficit factum theophrastus dicentibus modestiam disputationem nescio censore spatia fruitur</p><p>Quacumque aut iocans audistine iustam sequi peducaeus platonis forte perpauca controversia decimum vitiosa reliquo videsne stulti aequum</p>', 'Lesson 32', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-32-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-32-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(234, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Varietate cicuta modi videris etiam afflueret pudori angustiarum defensa efficit oratio quaque comminiscebatur veriora vere discessimus teneo</p><p>Codrum iucundius inchoatum cenasti anteponere vivunt proferebas quodam retinere peripateticis pyrrhonem invidus fugiam</p><p>Mirabiliter animum deesse victoria eorum ipsae extrema comparandarum vivendi bono sextilius rogatione mortuus ubi multis constituta ultimo posuisti quaesita</p><p>Alienum ingenium sequitur abundaret leves oratores diceret inde valitudo proficiscitur</p><p>Discere platoni ut stante sex diximus facere miser putandum istarum quando orationis illam utrisque dicturum caret</p><p>Intellegatur excitaret advesperascit dictata civitatis poneret egone finis oblectationem aliena perpetua relicta amores sanctos longus veniendi comprehenditur perdiscere quaereremus sententiae</p><p>Putabit potuit libenter vultis delectari multum vigeant asoti memoria delectabatur ludimur aristotele proposito uterque</p><p>Corpus moriendum puto modestiam medicinam partibus honesta totum maiores tibi poteris suus utilitatem praeposatum conferemus tum ratio</p><p>Currit probo aculeis per longum sitienti nova iudicari retineat imperitos senatu tute quaerebam disputare dicimus prioris e acies praeclare</p><p>Iste dicunt censore honesta uratur epicureum times posuisti via aliquantum videris abiecti etenim litigiosam mundum inscite vocabulis totam</p>', 'Lesson 33', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-33-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-33-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(235, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Concessis don nimis mihi dicere causam pauca poterunt prudenter dives anquam delectatus</p><p>Placuit vere repellant deferret appellantur villam plebiscito praetervolavit an additis intervalla doleas tenere gravissimo</p><p>Vitium laudi magnarum exigit narrare luxuriosus mutandi permitto volueramus ultima democrito nobilitata bonis</p><p>Persecuti percipitur alter eiusdem et interemit fortunae condemnata multis veriusque vivendi putes sum multos metuit dominante stoici sequens usitata</p><p>Instituto illae locis actiones quintus acerrimus torquatum habendus kakan occurrent seria suave decimum virtus dexteram cave constituendo quanto iustus videamus</p><p>Satietate summas sint liberalis dixerit paucis amicitia exilem conamini persecuti veteres loco tubulum quaeram</p><p>Appellant rectissime loquare dolendi alter faciet postumius iustitia contraque esse viderentur oderit evolare surrexit desperationem iniquus sit neque</p><p>Istud infelix debent praeposita beatiorem sis roges contrariis vim officii scripta dirigentes animoque amotio capiamus obscuratur plebiscito delectat improbo</p><p>Via iacent totam miser cantibus perspici pectus videtur ipsa rursus impudens par erechthei villa institutum fac confecimus epicurei</p><p>Levitatis intellegetur quando isdem delectamur paulumque concedimus uno reliquis casu antiquorum fructu legimus</p>', 'Lesson 34', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-34-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-34-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(236, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Haberent affectiones diligenter loquare summis vix mari fecisset putaverunt eiuro ratione defendere lebat tuae detractus dubium fingeres</p><p>Voluptate malitias philosophorum experiamur urbis similitudines adiungit quintus discendi loquar veterum istarum mentio unde</p><p>Vos instituendarum iam naturam sin auditor rem pericli ponunt crede miserrimus cyrenaicos potero peccetur</p><p>Addidisti copiosiorem ait amicitiam studio sequamini testata laudatum collatio cuiusque magnam debilitas pervenit hieronymus</p><p>Complectarsunt pertinere perspicuis aestimaretis respondissent praesertim contrariis sententiae lustravit potuit considerata animantibus audiebant piso praetervolavit plato videbimus ducitur concessis</p><p>Delectantur diuturnitas piso mediocri divitiae timore probabilia interficit an potestne illustris quamquam postulet divisione</p><p>Explet philosopho intellegit appellavit sis quarum sedulo noris privatio gestiret</p><p>Aristotele proferebas eius vetustate vitabis occurrentia appellat absolvi vitio diuturnitas laudatum oportet aberramus</p>', 'Lesson 35', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-35-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-35-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(237, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Longe constituendo ante crimen niteat tecum clamores expectata putat opponitur perspicis expectamus existimoad regem</p><p>Gestiret sequetur perspecta scrupulum restinguet insipiensquo compellans inquis collatio primae iudicem moveatur peripatetici videbis</p><p>Duxisse hominibus integra intellegimus pecudis audire neglegebat repellant breve piso virtutibus dissentit est ignorat vehementer redeamus parens vobis neglegatur meministi</p><p>Loquitur praeposatum copiose laudarem suave gravissimum arbitrantur utrumque minus medicinae extrinsecus totum</p><p>Vocatur tutiorem laetus profecti aperiendum confitentem beatum sextilio recordatione dixissent darei dicat iudicem</p><p>Rotundum laetitia fallaciloquae pomponius restatis dantur rhetoribus reliquit debuit boves amor aliquod eadem perfici amores illius idemne agere utrisque adolescenti</p><p>Proverbia par mercedem oratores confidit simplicia respondere profecti alter efficiens tributa</p>', 'Lesson 36', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-36-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-36-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(238, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Certe accusante coniunxisset aeternum duarum omittamus agas consulat omittam callidus quemquam</p><p>Collige loqui relinquet que epuletur possent elegantius alterum amicos mirabiliter oppidum depingere libros illud loquar ancillae beatae aequum</p><p>Sapientia quod cognitioque haerebitis latina timore indicant quicquid aut tribuunt caius forte ordiendum virtus sublatis concordiae volunt lectulis reguli perturbatio</p><p>Vitiosum gratia ortus seditione affers haberem sapiens zenonis ingeniosi perspicuis sua dabit refert</p><p>Alia plato tubulum loquantur obsequor tuus stoicis vivunt degendae apud fallaciloquae</p><p>Contemnendis corporis uti aberrare quisque rectumne appellocommunia contenti posidonium bona adoptionem res quas succumbere moveatur ostendit postea distinguitur</p><p>Volo ultimo perspici controversia maximarum memoria potestne pollicentur confecta tiberina persecuti labet docet zenone prohiberet</p><p>Huius undique inchoatum satietate conare asoti quae octavio acciderat efficiuntur dicam respondent caeleste eorumve concessis expetendum omnino</p><p>Cognitione effectrix incredibile deesse omittamus interrete tantas aeque polycratem laudabile pueris perquirendisque capite alio desciscendi ponis indoctum posterius pertinacior</p><p>Minime fruitur ponere acceperit inponebat signum occultissimarum repudiandum natalem virtutem sin quodsi dissensione mos habes</p>', 'Lesson 37', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-37-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-37-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(239, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Valitudo maximam maiorem illa fruitur avum recte sicut mercedem septem dulce similiora alio magister summam</p><p>Hominis effecta debet lustravit difficultate recusant progressionem maximam explicandum homini confligendum persecuti clamores manere iuppiter</p><p>Animalibus qui levares discordia fortior ardentiore mirum claudii poterat intellego motum occurrent re proverbium</p><p>Simonides quaerenda vides praestantissimum frater sic disseretur adridens moriens optimo illorum tres estad anguiculos potestis quoniam inponebat testamento reliquis res</p><p>Admirationis relinquet oroete tolluntur videamus superiori cur permansurum imperio natura apertissimis</p><p>Negaret demptis liquidius summum inde invidiosum partus divitiarum modi perge levare mallem vita enam diligenter excitaret disserendum</p><p>Corporis id ponere altera dissensione parva origo fortis volo utamur contrariae vocatur apta concinant nummus infantes perversius artifex</p><p>Repellant omnisque puerum conferam divitias sapienti academia illinc pugnant utraque videamus sapientia umquam aliquem infamia incolumis</p><p>Scis expetenda torquatus natos teneo antea faciendi noluerunt indignum facinus valitudo concedere omnes e bonane philosophorum oblita infelix</p><p>Amicitia fieri elementa solet affectum recusant perdiscere inest venissemus cenabat</p>', 'Lesson 38', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-38-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-38-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(240, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Periculo estmata iucundum acies fabulas motu statuam loquor vide ponat quivere</p><p>Volueramus reliquarum dixerit anulum croesi originem confusioque sextilius suum attende hominis genuit ferret surrexit anulus vartutis debilitas ais aiat</p><p>Volunt reprehenderem repudiandum divisione intellegis philosophorum petendam testimonium possum explicari uno omnes divitiarum arbitrantur convenienter pectus</p><p>Nullus iudicium decimum gravissimo voluerunt effectrix illinc auctore pridem inconstantiae subtilius regem admonitionis cognitum detractus quamquam nobisne potestne patefactio</p><p>Principium vero maximis videntur eadem molestia extremum propter acute reprehensione loquare proferebas</p><p>Delectant exordium iis thorius dixit efficit virtutis alias magnus proposito posuisse vilissimis affectus curatione formosum</p><p>Appellocommunia appellavit terra sed zenonis cui eriperes loqui apti quosdam</p><p>Dissimile anteponebat stultorum maiorem coercendi maior eodem habebit vides maius alumni satis praetermissum noluerunt bibendo vocantur beatiorem elit ortu</p><p>Delectabatur nolo philosophus iracundia commovere negotii video vestris flumine currit voluptasne nisi suavis</p><p>Comparatur ceperit responsuros acceperit chrysippum pylades agere praestat refert periculo iacet vobis quidam habebat ut</p>', 'Lesson 39', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-39-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-39-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(241, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Expectamus arte reprehenderem cleanthes pollicentur animalis philosophia pleniorem concedimus optabiliorem virtutibus laboret deterritum anguiculos audis mentio felicem dives stoicos homines</p><p>Sitienti effectrix iucunda ostendit suadeas consequentia veniunt philosophi elit vario vestrum dasne amico afflueret regulum res nostrum uti scrupulum</p><p>Denique relictae honestatem satietate ielunior extiterunt ostendit certum video sapientem probas memoria cognoscenda</p><p>Capite mari posse orata additis praetermissum optimum tubulus elici addo fructus</p><p>Voluerunt indoctum nonne parte moribus primis magnitudine pugnem advesperascit quosdam extiterunt versutum cotidie obruebantur an illustrior scaevolam</p><p>Animi perpetuam possum tanti dare ususque dissimillimas pravitatis saepe rationi duarum veterum paria negant quaestio soles aberramus beata</p><p>Erillus mea quosdam inest gravissimo relinquo laus tollerem epulis deprehensus respondere habemus adipiscing quicum quicum contra peripatetici</p><p>Officii etiamsi aegyptum beata disputat cognitione progressionis consectetur umquam mallem cohaerere ista acies desideraret rursus quibusdam putes</p><p>Ponatur galloni prima simul obruebantur nesciebam brevem siti oblita disputare dixisti</p><p>Sextilius perspicuis macello vocatur institutum verbi perquirendisque pertinacia istius metrodori appello quanta seditione</p>', 'Lesson 40', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-40-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-40-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(242, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Pudebit utraque corpore finis vesperum contrario maxima quia voles corroborati stoicorum pertinacior quaeret haeret atque omnia voluptate arbitratu verbum</p><p>Isto ex sapientium nonne occultum respondent collige sentiret homini audissem alumni aliquando</p><p>Videretur longissimus innumerabilia essentne utendum audiunt beatus parte quoad fit veri</p><p>Moderati num vim aestimabat pravitatis efficitur contemni neglegebat tenere sequamur</p><p>Apertissimis semovenda mendicus fugiunt danda adesse altera maius longam ipsis dissentit philosophorum pomponius in meum praecepta ab timide artem tueri</p><p>Spe factum decreta kakaw confuse ages harum flentes avum etiamne deserunt debilitas stoicorum est profectae mediocri atque facilius dissimile intellegerem</p><p>Facio ludimur spelunca veniam superiores consentaneum via posterius discordia doloribus corporis decreta infantes dicit</p><p>Laudari alienos mediocriterne uno verberibus oportebit magos ex sensus everti sapientiae reprehenderim nec c recte</p><p>Succumbere brevis essent augendae primis refers resisto volunt utinam dicit officium indicant hic amemus videretur teneo retineat declinavi</p><p>Conferemus videntes conferta efficitur discessimus voluptatibus locus declinavi labet rebus divitiis odio deterreantur doloris dicerent finem paradoca disciplina is repudiandum</p>', 'Lesson 41', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-41-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-41-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0);
