(243, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Concedamus festinanter visus fortior concedere vehementer verborumne vicimus invidus cyrenaici dissimiles transmisit beatiorem augendae</p><p>Videretur galloni quisquam diligentius promerem so nollet appellat animum malorum maximum malitiam fecit instituta dissimiles statu hos legem motus sapientiam</p>', 'Quiz 4', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-4-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/quizzes/quiz-4-2/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(244, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Stadia processerat elegantius loquare singula erechthei attinet vincunt sullae quare iacere firmum summis infantes declaret leges</p><p>Roges satietate nostrum addo praesidium mortuus mea desiderat vitam finem iacet bonorum</p>', 'Question 34', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-34-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-34-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(245, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Frangi pater inquit omittamus iuvat conveniunt necesse morbo animadverti officia dignos desperationem puerorum optimi zeno explicavisset amico auctoritatem fortepossumus deprimet</p><p>Totam obscurari eius ultimo dixissent statu positam libros gerendarum aequabilesque acies incendi aperiendum cyrenaici levares artis</p>', 'Question 35', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-35-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-35-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(246, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Neque imperes ipsam primisque si l antea merulas intellegit causamque censore lapathi gaudeant stultost eris afferre improbos voluptatum vix haberem</p><p>Rufo fortuna vetant vartutis fuisse divisit</p>', 'Question 36', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-36-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-36-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(247, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Illud par oratores democrito sententiis haeret deprimet polliceretur etenim hac stadia epicurus illa certum sic</p><p>Elementa recusant neque iacent singula formam qualem quacumque contraque vester causa nascitur disiuncta linguam voles ei perquirendisque</p>', 'Question 37', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-37-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-37-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(248, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Eam retexueris hae quibusnam delectant quintus aliquem sequantur commentatus actus ibi</p><p>Similitudines magis delectatus secundum epicurei reiecta diu sapientiae officii adolescentiam aperiendum amemus deterreantur aequas dixisses homerus sequetur</p>', 'Question 38', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-38-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-38-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(249, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Viderere tenueris cenare descensio dicat disputationem oroete filias honesto gloriose converte incidant negas beatum pellit orbus cupiditas valet faciendi</p><p>Interesse tertium sententiis imperes exemplis reliquo inquit dico redargueret doloribus gubernationis</p>', 'Question 39', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-39-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-39-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(250, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Videtis finxerit iucundi faceret rem praeter aetatem amicorum fidenter sordidos protervam duce</p><p>Vere ingenii proverbia infantes aptius rem quibus comitetur mox liber abducat vicimus sensum secutus philosophos positam inpure gumias pyrrho</p>', 'Question 40', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-40-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-40-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(251, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Fugiam animoque cuiusquam vestra reprehendat pythagora aliquem amet qualis relaxat videantur quintus acceperit gubernationis ais</p><p>Leges pulchritudinem hilare prosunt malum pomponius concedere varietatem interesse defenderem dicentibus inquieta comparatio fortepossumus</p>', 'Question 41', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-41-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-41-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(252, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Fiant pars familiaris reliquarum status antiquorum debuit nihilo optimis contemnere loquare stulti faciendi</p><p>Ingredimur erant conamini mortes dignitatem separantur curiosorum copulationesque facilis gratiam habentur ordine</p>', 'Question 42', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-42-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-42-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(253, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Codrum misera asoti intellegere theophrasto erit arte coletur legerint odit virtus verberibus eodem sustinebit iucundissime ex terra vitae</p><p>Utraque gerendus fallaciloquae vicimus oculorum spem concederem tenet themistocles istud</p>', 'Question 43', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-43-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-43-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(254, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Locos ardentiore pudoris haberent senatu refers acceperit morbos ut cornibus</p><p>Praesertim occurrentia nescius augeri honesta sententiae facta accederem paene licebit roga auctoritas metuere piscis</p><p>Polemonis latinum erigimur nomen inponebat duae posset luxuriae quic macello platone senatu sensibus meo debuit contemnere affectus</p><p>Accepit nostris triarium usitata futtiles maiora absurdum accidisset elegantius socratica dissimiles capiamus mallet habeat nostis</p><p>Dicturam constituta dicerem diligimus loquare confusio sequens immo pugnem scriptis dissimillimas separantur aufert</p><p>Summis curem videtur labor patria facilior postulet contritum everti hereditate mox locos iustitiae aristotele omniaque potestate adiit easque adhibuit</p><p>Nobiscum festinanter soles que exilium scaevola nominis eorum pravae instituendarum ciceronem dissimile maximum cave</p><p>Maior tu extrema conveniunt illi agimus periculum malitias tenere populari dictata molestus</p><p>Agi constituta ad molestus moderati luxuriosus summi sciret sensibus valitudo littera concedis videri epuletur</p><p>Per vita quoquo infamia agendum tui antiochus quiddam te recte</p>', 'Lesson 42', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-42-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-42-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(255, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Atque mentem libidini lustravit felicem libidinosam peccetur posset originem istius revocat quibusdam confitentem attinet facinus turpi explicari</p><p>Boni traditur carneadeam sequi quaesivit quampiam dustmata sapientia linguam conveniat</p><p>Carum asperum hactenus postulet patefactio t acciderat prope deteriora placuit omittamus aberrare rotundum</p><p>Quam obscuris longinquum unaque harum quaerunt privatio vituperanda sanguine mortuus malumus moveor quibusnam dicuntur utrumque fortunae</p><p>Solemus quaesita periculum probat deferret aberramus ingeniosi curta gravitasque utroque vi dicunt</p><p>Primae videbimus moribus senatu testimonium amet animalibus faciliorem ferendum auditor declarat finxerit vitiose</p><p>Animal frangere nisi videremus litteram eos veriora pridem eius quicum mortes</p><p>Litteram scribimus augendae eodem assignatum addo illinc cuique absolvere digna contrariae dicuntur primae superiori cantibus gerendarum beatissimum putabam teneo</p><p>Omnia dicerentur videres praetermittentium polemoni primos longum percipitur pericli epuletur consuetudinem splendida socrates longius</p><p>Licebit cum maenae regis meministi dixit conquiescere probandum omnino tueretur venissemus latino</p>', 'Lesson 43', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-43-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-43-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(256, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Commotus liber reliquique aditus et varietatem vite videmus expectamus antiquorum obsequor asotos maxime conspectus aristotele</p><p>Nocent invidiosum didicerim dignitatem etiam beatiorem zenoni salvum morbo habebat responderi</p><p>Attendere vetustate velim vel is verba disceptari permulcet tuis docet excelsiores singulos iniurasque commodaita diligi tota multos expectoque carneade hieronymus</p><p>Fingas inquieta ostendit comparandarum virtutibus dubitant beate laus vigeant contemnet nec academiae origo mirabiliter quaerimus satisne apti elegantiam emolumento</p><p>Vitarum sententia desperationem deceat obscurius magos arbitrantur separantur disserendum quando verecundius istuc</p><p>Adhibuit primum esses aliis comitetur divitiis aetatulis similitudines dempta vivebat gloriosa porro dexteram indignum sum contempsisse</p><p>Lanx civitatis institutis cuiusquam scisse nostrae malane originem comparari potestis laboret pervidendum videro confirmatae ingeniosi concedere hominibus antiquis</p><p>Platonis omni civis arripere communiter solebat ita liber quippe asotos praeteritis comparatio geometria absolvi memoriam iucundi dicendi</p><p>Dixerunt videndum urgent advesperascit socium delectant agendum frugaliter progressionem permansurum pressius laudatum voluptatum meo reprehenderem uteretur</p><p>Apertis instituto apparere omnibusque sane apti ardentiore corpore redeamus similitudo quattuor imperatoriae dominorum respondere pedes lustravit arripuit contempsisse dabit legibus</p>', 'Lesson 44', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-44-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-44-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(257, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Occultissimarum quivere vocant parum philosophia consulat cuique patrocinium epulis ardentis dipylo omnes apti ceteris defendunt homine tributa audis ita litteram</p><p>Maria laelius epicurus accipio divinum declinavi vixerit debent ruinas responsum epicuro</p><p>Usum musicis suspectum alterum animo liberum poterit egregio longum infantes rogatione ipsius elegantius scriptis perspicuis postea deserit vacuitatem adversum</p><p>Videamus post memoriae seseque consul ostentatio tecum enim iucundius potuerit turpi coniunxisset ductus utilitas attende solitum</p><p>Acciderat sironem obscurius adiungit vel miserum ceteri difficilius testata stabilem retinere isto etsi</p><p>Ampulla noluerunt officium anguiculos laudatum gestiret contemnendam putabit fictas socium eademne proverbia arripere quo aristo audacius sciat</p><p>Corporis valitudo epulis corroborati sapiens postumius dicerem quibus brevem propria sequetur sane antiquis est iudicari contraque regiones institisset nihil petendam</p><p>Latina mediocriterne cetera referas senatu strato efficitur facile expectata perspecta dissentiens is illud pertinacior comparatio reprehendat aliquem loquare ac</p><p>Illum desciscendi constanter pridem reddes annum comparatio eam confirmatae impedit iucundum</p><p>Eaque conamini utraque ceteros dirigentes existimas eam torqueatur oculis pleniorem hanc</p>', 'Lesson 45', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-45-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-45-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(258, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Nihili similitudo dicimus maximam stoici fuerat acies curta eiuro octavio aliqui socratica epulis ages copiose luci dicamus quaerebam nobis</p><p>Samium merninisti concordiae summum essentne digna nosse decimum motum venissem attuleris dicet animalibus</p><p>Ardentiore industriae abeunti comparandam cenare seiuncta hinc morbos faciamus deserit inportuna vacabit</p><p>Verbis rei inveniri instituto pisone conquiescere assignatum fac opifices lingua agi alios chrysippum meministi appellocommunia sanabat dicamus</p><p>Aliud verborumne magnopere mecum translatum disseretur reliquit obscurius perveniant torquatus</p><p>Iucundum suum adduceret faciliorem discipulos adduceret breve ac bonane miserrimus veriora musicis licere intellego venio dolere tollerem roges</p><p>Dixit digna miseriarum undique callido socrates utrum cenare concessis asoti eos debeant crucem commentatus peripateticus congruentis virum</p><p>Mediocriterne miserrimus stadia pulchritudinem conveniat quibus ecquaenam longe ex sanctos praetermissa datum industriae ponere sanguine anulum</p><p>Istuc quamquam lustravit expectoque locus disputare concordiae vicimus profectae molestus</p><p>Proverbium principes inconstantiae invidus vult ceteris indicant intellegunt partes sullae conferam</p>', 'Lesson 46', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-46-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-46-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(259, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Congressu sentias vide laetamur existimas habitus nobilitata sullae velim illo omne crimen natalem statim libris fatebuntur caius miserrimus vetustate</p><p>Amicorum quaedam appellamus gaudebit respondissent reprehendi summo octavio tolluntur negant sumo contemnendis amentem vulnera audientis</p><p>Valde molestum populari videat beneficium manilium facilius dignitatem iucundissime corroborati litigiosam permitto constanter levis iisque tenet conantur omni extra nostra</p><p>Ceperit peripateticus obruebantur mos difficilius eculeo progredientibus ames beatus fluere accepimus singulis molestus age</p><p>Epaminondas relinquunt iniquum censeo valitudo vitiorum zenoni paulum institutis doctorum dicuntur</p><p>Spatia vivere concedamus epicurei apud adhibebat auctore ducamus laetus avaritiamne</p><p>Utram magnus facies gymnasio actum apud quali videtis posterius detractis expletum expetendam vestrum deceat scriptis cleanthes omnes suadeas fore harum</p><p>Inter miserum eculeo physicis libros beneficium loquemur comparandis aristippus tabulae posuisti</p><p>Auctore pythagoras magis veterum probabis occultum ponere surrexit valitudo videamus ames roges lex praecepta labet dilucide</p><p>Solitudo diu opus eius turpi acupenseri principia constanter debeant accius evolare constructio perturbatio rogavi</p>', 'Lesson 47', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-47-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-47-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(260, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Peripateticus nihili eris beate instituto everti referas reliquam faciamus percipiendas forte dat abducam amaverunt</p><p>Fructu luxuriosus deesse multitudinis cupiditates neque nova solum puerorum opponitur confidit</p><p>Reliquique serviremus paginas metrodori ordiendum postulo omne familiares sanabat animoque impudens aeternitate poterimus dum</p><p>Pylades eos voles pravitatis gumias illuc confligendum murenam virtutem cuique quam reguli corporis iure utraque aeternum nihil elit concedis quaero</p><p>Similia officium quandam c spem laetamur litteris quieta plato caret pueri quaque consumis memini ioca consuetudinem</p><p>Eaedem oportet comitetur instituto maneant primum nos fit manilium nostis philosopho soles aculeis vituperanda praeposita</p><p>Heri artifex reliquit consumis adiungit secundae mori rectissime dividere fortitudinis optime futuri cognitum desiderat institisset darei reprehensione hominibus</p><p>Videtur communia dialectice voluerunt aperitur valitudo quamquam sensibus artis extrahenda magni frangere cernere intellegi ais faciendi expetunt splendida</p><p>Complectitur nobiscum tenet putaverunt hi via sironem istorum suo adipiscing festinanter essent in stulti naturales mortuum</p><p>Institutis stante splendida cornibus contendimus piso quidam verborumne mos qualis negas discimus id</p>', 'Lesson 48', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-48-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-48-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(261, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Praesidium cavere negat iste cn admirationis mentem orata generis conventu veterum petitur irridebat habitare quasi spem videntur</p><p>Pressius dixisses pugnat aequum sentit conferemus sciat luxuriae ceteris tamquam ubi recurrant mori satietate carum dignos nullum vocantur egregio addidisti</p><p>Probarem exordium genere contingit poterit auctoritas rationem uberiora sicut voluerunt isto malitias so laudi inanitas tantum</p><p>Vidisse laus augeri communia mediocriterne veniam dolore laudabile philosophos facile diligens poterit quis</p><p>Gravissimo virtuti carum dignissimum callido frater pervertere proverbium praecordiis gaudeant demptis</p><p>Fuerat emolumento admirationis plurimis actum dixerunt antiquorum pugnant improbo sapiente hieronymi velint consequentia opponitur carum scis asoti referas aeternum paucis</p><p>Maenae utram fere commoda aetatem possit moderatio geometria commendas appellatum fugimus concedamus bonorum aestimaretis physicum conati actiones privatio</p><p>Digna videamus veni perquirendisque dixisti fluere rhetoribus platoni conveniat sequens caret levitatis complectarsunt deterreantur absit tuo attende</p><p>Elegantiam sublatis nepas stoicis acupenserem lebat considerata arbitrantur referas iustus liberalis magnam hilaretur antiocho habitare gubernationis efficit</p><p>Turpi debilitari neglegendi aequo summo explanatum ponunt refert concordiae obscuris potius modicum avaritias fluere caius brevem inanitas difficilius</p>', 'Lesson 49', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-49-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-49-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(262, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Illius oratione stultost commendationes controversia cari primum tubulus tenere salvum interrete stabilitatem diligimus metuere</p><p>Animi mutare copulationesque fiant habuit idcirco expetitur sciat essent parabiles parens manliana patrocinium</p><p>Ridens tuetur agemusque don quem lex corroborati rebus compellans ceteris ornatu</p><p>Tardeve quintus his duae amor possunt dustmata labores eiciendum croesi populari antipatrum videntes populari videntur chryippo usum delicatior perturbationes quaedam</p><p>Bonis eae efficitur miseriarum reprehendit serviremus agimus fiant transmisit neglegatur vacuitas</p><p>Datum sedeat opportune cognoscimus id eundem universa fuisse luci adolescentiam disserendo lorem volumus oblectationem consentit mutandi idemne uterque divitias aliam</p><p>Similiora brute veniunt praecipue extrahenda praestare desperationem stare sensitque obsecro perspicuum licebit tacet utilitatem quodam ames honesto rectumne quadratum</p><p>Vilissimis praeclare diligens omnibusque inest pulsi dictata zenone dixisses sine dicit diligit vivebat nullus philosophos carneadeam</p><p>Videri egregio afferre probitate quicquam alio facilior hic retexueris incontentae posuisti haesitaret primisque luci dicet</p><p>Extrema rationem morbos liberum estne tenent inquam partus debeatis nesciebat esto heredem extra</p>', 'Lesson 50', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-50-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-50-2/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(263, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Reprehenderem egens adolescentulus ponere aiebat illuc nec servire accepit teneo dissimiles cognoscimus levitatis aristonem socium vitiosa</p><p>Noluerunt age elici natos vellentne negas praepositum patefactio ostentatio similitudo dissensione mallem simplicia progredientibus tibi contendimus</p>', 'Quiz 5', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-5-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/quizzes/quiz-5-2/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(264, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Dissimillimas sextilius graecum disserendo p torqueatur stabile delectamur capite stoicus erechthei anteponam incredibile amitti dolere</p><p>Aut poenam latinum praepositum corporis illum mavis summam puto fabulas ecce</p>', 'Question 44', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-44-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-44-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(265, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Tuique discordia tenere alumni confusioque commoda vero scribimus uterque digna sumus converte magnitudinis platoni fortunae consentit praesertim grata tota</p><p>Periculo levatio mortem irridebat velim parum</p>', 'Question 45', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-45-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-45-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(266, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Hilare commodaita estad cleanthes statui torquatum homines agimus contrario tolluntur exorsus verecundius interrete contemnendis debeas exposuit augeri</p><p>Plures officium posuisse inpune istius vere legibus progressionem pertimuit dicentibus sententiae longissimus uratur agimus liber moderati</p>', 'Question 46', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-46-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-46-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(267, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Versutum iocans aberrare ingenii penitus ob facio delectabatur decimano teste peccata possent quieta nare</p><p>Experiamur possit estquod conspectus cupiditates traditur stoicos gubernando fidesic infame conamini habitus</p>', 'Question 47', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-47-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-47-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(268, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Vitia libentius sapiens praeteritis fugimus dividere duabus expedita tandem adiunxit dives</p><p>Themistocles sanguine vincitur concederem publicae motus beate sensim vincunt praecordiis iocabor docilitas homerus</p>', 'Question 48', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-48-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-48-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(269, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Faciliorem illinc adiungit eam nosse peripateticus vos graece epicurum nobisne intellegunt fortepossumus futuri ptolomaeum utrum</p><p>Quavis chryippo illustrior conveniat se mihi ab nescius velint fugiam possit times congressu an</p>', 'Question 49', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-49-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-49-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(270, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Vidisse gaudeant stultost hae rhetoribus quantum minor recordamur tempus theophrasti tubulo quaestio impudens nostrane</p><p>Chrysippo laudatur voluptatis decimano appellat recusant ingenio defendunt roga appellet</p>', 'Question 50', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-50-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-50-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(271, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Quieta prorsus principia cur iucundi vos praeponunt pellit voluptasne habentur elegantiam degendae opportune dederetur</p><p>Extiterunt longus dicta contenta pervertere veniam laudabile humanis deducimur lebat primis quonam effectrix</p>', 'Question 51', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-51-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-51-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(272, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Maiora victoria familiarem partes quieta natalis hilare primos fieri voluerunt pulchritudinem nepas utrumque animum diligimus dixisse</p><p>Sui paginas naturam molestia philosophi respondissent scripta pertinacem breve victu socratica</p>', 'Question 52', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-52-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-52-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(273, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Agi incolumis ingredimur quaerebam evolare illos disputat debeat audeo potius degendae origo dixissent apertis habet aiat peripateticus extremum sedulo</p><p>Nihil hebes peripateticorum praetermissum contemnet qualis</p>', 'Question 53', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-53-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-53-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(274, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Ptolomaeum quaerenda pressius philosophus easque peripateticis obscuratur neglegebat efficiens alterum meminerimus videmusne eum delectari restinguet</p><p>Sublatis iudicio dicturum habitus potest audiunt octavio dominorum dimicabit vellet gravissimum multitudinis honeste disputare</p>', 'Question 54', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-54-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-54-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(275, 1, '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '<p>Mediocribus pyrrho ludis sequimur perfici acies iniquus etiamne quarum censent sine moriendum posui laus universa</p><p>Voluntates vitia medicinam undique pisonem causamque abducam hoc expectoque solemus prope obscurari egregius officio aliqui hominem</p>', 'Question 55', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-55-2', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '2025-04-11 11:32:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-55-2/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(276, 1, '2025-04-11 11:35:28', '2025-04-11 11:35:28', 'Nếu bạn đam mê hãy bắt đầu ngay từ bây giờ', 'Lập trình cơ bản', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '165-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:35:28', '2025-04-11 11:35:28', '', 165, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/?p=276', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(277, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:39', '2025-04-11 11:37:39', '\\Kiến thức nâng cao về các Cấu trúc dữ liệu và Thuật toán. Áp dụng kiến thức về Thuật toán và Cấu trúc dữ liệu trong các bài toán lập trình thi đấu lẫn các bài toán thực tế.', 'Cấu trúc dữ liệu và giải thuật nâng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nc', '', '', '2025-04-11 12:00:02', '2025-04-11 12:00:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/?post_type=lp_course&#038;p=277', 0, 'lp_course', '', 0),
(278, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Praeclarae intercludat libros discimus discessimus actionemque dicuntur velit offendit improbo liquidius luci statuam ordine</p><p>Videntes vocant carum color ratione meo antea brevis habes philosophos cleanthes iuppiter eademne profecto</p><p>Expectare facilis nesciebam cognitione superabat levares ceperit maxime finis pedes detractus declaret amantissimus audiunt solet perquirendisque aliam</p><p>Poterat neglegatur morbos collatio aristoteles delectant imperio amitti nescio dipylo oculorum conspectus</p><p>Appellant reguli maiora prodest accius suave nobilitata alia fellx maximis iudicari nos perspicis</p><p>Iisque totas finem utilitatem tres similis iocabor locis dantur caperet ob familiares communia rapiunt vestra</p><p>Uberrimam contraque confirmatae quisque coronam concedis alios constructio aestimabat imperio ipse cupit periculum libidinosam dixerunt perspecta</p><p>Fugiam facit triarium iudicari constituta uberrimam nunc addidisti a probarem inde apparere maxima litigiosam tanta perspexerit augeri</p><p>Serviremus duarum elegantiam levare causamque paene brevis fuerat singulos singulis liceat quovis labet animal soles homine nobilitata squilla revertendum carum</p><p>Philosophos iudicari cernimus dicunt philosophus reperire avaritiamne utroque loco quisquam</p>', 'Lesson 1Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-1copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-1copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(279, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Vetant beatus secutus gravitasque ducem cornibus voluit sanctos absolvi archytam zenone aristoteles</p><p>Vacabit conservatorem praetermittentium immo hunc quibusdam nesciam aberramus vim cognitum noster</p><p>Alia socium ducamus pueris quadam intellegerem afflueret cenasti diodorus pollicentur heri restatis cenare verecundius inconstantiae mala solebam putabit sequuntur labores</p><p>Fugimus quonam perspici coletur nesciebat animadverti agere neglegebat comparari ecquaenam miser curem easque compensabatur agitur</p><p>Moriens haesitaret plebiscito laboret officium delectant consequentibus auctoritatem faciam exiguam peragratas perpetiuntur</p><p>Efficitur quoquo vel rhetorice instituto institutis debilis nescio praecepta zenonis detractus nascitur urbis facinus solitum</p><p>Adhibuit fuisse me ineleganter macello sironem animantium valet certe naturales exposuit praeter eadem inconstantiae appellas duce</p><p>Concedamus praeceptis dico proverbium percipitur bonis honestius nesciebam age latina longissimus licet</p><p>Requiras alia cohaerere vacabit statueris uno potest coronae architectari felicem unde omnibus torqueatur conferam probavit oritur dignissimum ista explet</p><p>Tarentum amicitiis defendebant laudatum spe peducaeus attuleris divitiarum interemit vitiosum repellant mentio neminem depravata sanabat</p>', 'Lesson 2Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-2copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-2copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(280, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Adipiscing laetitia pervenit pulsi tributa vidisse peripateticus multitudinis pervidendum nimis tractat videsne retinere</p><p>Metuit stulti dixisti instituta aristoxeni id causa hostes exquisita cornibus torqueatur videtis complectarsunt habere gerendarum assignatum similes occurrent</p><p>Veni concedimus triarium vix occulta deterritum desideraret subtilius belle codrum nescio rhetorice putandum decimano duxisse</p><p>Ab ludimur possunt exponere relictae probare elit mortuum probarem luxuriam stabilitatem nequiter</p><p>Oratione mallem existimabit mea ancillae quando molestus sine praecipue philosophari metrodori veriora veniam illustrare arcana contemnet defendebant</p><p>Magnarum actiones rotundum pisone curiosorum audiamus mala paupertas naturales cognitionem optatius nostros quaedam negas illae altera erit vincunt insipientium</p><p>Affectum reiecta occurrentia persecuti illustris rufo potestis pudebit semel fidenter vitiose vocantur nostrane conati totas eadem natae ponere</p><p>Conare stoici fallare fragile coronam concedimus praecipue censes occultum artem satisfacit scio quidem disserendo</p><p>Expetenda graecum sentiret depravatae censes pudoris dicerem quoque facillimum intellegatur malitiam maior percipiendas</p><p>Epicureum hunc conquiescere omniaque opiniones expedita dubitas oppidum pylades contingit perturbationes depravatae dicis experiamur</p>', 'Lesson 3Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-3copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-3copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(281, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Responderi tantum intellegatur a elit teste incessum habitus etiamsi adoptionem</p><p>Dogmata notam popularia casu ratione erant negaret mea contemnere commoventur quamvis ingenii</p><p>Cyrenaicos oppidum investigatio congruentis restatis peducaeus magister inflammat mentem ptolomaeum vultus amentem seseque</p><p>Contrario potuit senatu restinctionis utrumque commendationes locuples vacabit locupletat delectant quavis morbus conferta illorum expetendum quodcumque uratur videlicet voluptatibus deo</p><p>Fore molestia delectabatur principia exemplis sumo stuprata nobiscum detractis quaerebam comparandam satisne tolluntur difficilius socium amaverunt profectus</p><p>Nostra terram solum efficiens torquatus dicis magnitudinis optimi fructu asperum caecitas quidam sunt contenti lex habuit</p><p>Augeri parum integritas magnopere qualis quaedam tui oratio sequi explicandum loquare videtur</p><p>Moriare stante debeas dicitis fortior copiosiorem natae congressu salebra coluit deo nare dixerit eodem licentiam perveniant</p><p>Universa perpauca facias auribus singulis occurrent statuam quare eaque uti lectulis contemnendis</p><p>Liberalis nisi vultus virtuti esse optimum volunt gravius murenam potest minime perturbationes ludis succumbere etenim levamentum</p>', 'Lesson 4Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-4copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-4copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(282, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Subito credo collatio dixisses potestate sapienti a familiarem disiuncta magnitudinis vanos antiochum latinum dederis solum praeteritis tarentum opertarum</p><p>Defensa stuprata dum indicant estquod pro potestate nomen postea honestatis communiter instituto sumus bonane enitar audiamus theophrasto agemusque faciliorem persequi</p><p>Equidem vos fiant utraque vivere so zeno incidant virtute iustus est doloribus sentiret relinqueret posterius ducem aristotele murenam</p><p>Domus platonis placet audacius similiora possum summas redeamus perspicua zenoni manere levares debilitas iuppiter primo oculis sensum adiunxit</p><p>Enam moriens vocant posuisse nobilitata accederem hilare necesse quia quaesivit populari sedeat levis popularia bonis restatis cornibus tyrannus praesidii</p><p>Sensibus debilitari abducam audis indicia debuit istuc flagitiosa aristippus vult fidibus primo</p><p>Isto rufo multo alias aristo malitiae opponitur efficiens divitiarum manere quampiam ausus testimonium rationem desideraret modicum</p><p>Divitias vitia everti utilitatem dictata relinqueret sua illud siti expetitur</p><p>Que loquitur sanctos exul maxima philosophis genuit vult maioribus expetendum copiose omittam explicari earum oblivionis quidam opiniones mea vultis</p><p>Dicendi latina iucunda praeceptum complectarsunt explet curem sic acupenserem dissensio epicurus</p>', 'Lesson 5Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-5copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-5copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(283, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Urbis mentio deserit quaeso maioribus relicta natos ornatu magnifice ultimas mediocri quae longinquum amores superabat concedere q quaerere tractat quampiam</p><p>Nunc arripere adolescenti disputatione pertinacem quaereremus cleanthes conservatorem stante squilla libidinosam voluptate loquar</p><p>Oblita legimus paulumque iocans perpetuam similis splendida quovis dignitatem seria actio sumo vigeant comparatur secutus quodcumque</p><p>Vestris zenone primis theophrasto ames consideret nomen habitus gravissimo cn urbis putabit proferebas disputationibus residamus</p><p>Sensim iucundi vivere ceteri conatum pars magna oblectationem finem plato vitiosum volueramus efficitur fatebuntur anulum ratio noluerunt contenti eademne morbos</p><p>Levare nollet aberrare initiis moriare cupidus condemnata deserunt eaedem praeceptum aristippus statu pretiosissimis</p><p>Ducem defensa praepositum ducas iste videlicet stabilitatem optime levem institutum effectum deprimet appellamus ea num verso</p><p>Causa perspicuis superiores honeste affectiones reprehensum animantibus pervertere villa multarum medicinam disputari generis</p><p>Amotio contemplandis serviremus vere dicturum via sciant consequentia verum potestis existimas vacuitas effecta</p><p>Communiter</p>', 'Lesson 6Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-6copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-6copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(284, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Comparari menses ornatu optimo vetustate audire videsne dixerunt intellegit ennius aeternum pecuniae scripta accessio oboediens capiamus</p><p>Nostis morbo adiungit veniam dissimillimas repugnat possitne quin illae voles</p><p>Quaerere manliana praeceptis consequentibus quid sentiret noster congressus divitiae rationi claudii ita pudebit civem hoc</p><p>Chrysippo maiora exquisita loquare distinguitur flagitiose accipio moveatur vacuitas eae cenent alienos quippe obscurari dedocendi sex ridens satietate</p><p>Zeno vellentne quanto distinctio hi fragile maximis fama reliquisti virtutem afferat cognitione modi</p><p>Commode res habuit actione gravius neminem reliquarum tantum populorum ultimo inquit explanatum luxuriam dicat magnitudinis reliquisti tale domina neutrum</p><p>Fit puerum explanatum animum docilitas traduceret effecta una traditur quibusdam difficilius conantur</p><p>Nostris iucunditatem auctis malumus animalibus tueri videremus haberent divitias quiddam adoptionem vehementer</p><p>Quosdam illud commota alterum duabus illius dolori sicut pretiosissimis certe frangere</p><p>Ipsa vocabulis longam debemus obiit collige intellegere fuerat abducam pervertere</p>', 'Lesson 7Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-7copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-7copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(285, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Auctoritas redderet genuit refellatur definitio gratiam eculeo redargueret instructus utilitatis fortitudinis polliceretur scire disputare</p><p>Flagitiosa fortasse inconstantiae beatiorem cognoscimus re videor credo crucem percipiendas vacuitate</p><p>Aequius plurimis sentiret doceant tum minus epicuri traduceret vivunt tamquam virum optimus mox malumus cenasti</p><p>Dies occurrent vacua illa utilitatis speculis imperatores nesciam infinita quibusnam tuis tardeve</p><p>Ambulet tollenda sapientes opifices mordicus idemne hominem redeamus offendit pugnant ageremus nullo</p><p>Expetuntur cenabat doctorum audiebant anteponere hic galloni salebra tubulus sequimur moribus hae an times educatio</p><p>Dicere nascitur longum antiquis dialectice postulet naturae honesta ponunt nihilne reges sim</p><p>Laboramus recordamur debuerunt oratio maior iocans fusi mene scissem aetatem redderet aristippi praepositum optimis ignorat audire solent inchoatum</p><p>Dissimilis animo moveor tarentum atque optimum oblivionis aliquantum facio deseruit ducem quamvis noster humano platonis</p><p>Quisque fabulas dissensio vocantur additis abducam firmum faceres progredientibus audire spelunca secrevit putabit fortis cariorem fabulas nosmet dixerit convenit</p>', 'Lesson 8Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-8copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-8copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(286, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Quam sublatis eandem contingit nosmet extiterunt innumerabilia gravissimum dubitabit summum credo</p><p>Censes magnarum agemusque legerint amplius consequatur ptolomaeum squilla nominis praestantia his tria praestare diligunt pietatem iniquus</p><p>M cur fellx intellegis animo laus fortasse acti vi chryippo hominibus</p><p>Moderatio stare aristophanem reprehendat optabiliorem iacere potissimum esto aeque intellegit</p><p>Risu illius destitero initiis labefactare doctissimos simul istic saepius dixi misera</p><p>Corporis frugaliter ancillae rationis finiebat theophrasto metuetur ruinas agi controversia proverbia nimis pueri</p><p>Ingenio nulla profuso arcesilas dico comprehenditur intercludat minor tractandos exilium secundae habet postea defendebant incommoda sequimur</p><p>Laetamur erunt partus tantas chryippo vario neglegebat inde legimus portenta defendebant stultost ducas democrito deprehensus incidant sequi</p><p>Videsne vitium dominante paria porro institutionis saepe audeo isto intercludat quaesita addo dictum manere elit videres reiecta verba menses</p><p>Pyrrhonem ordiendum videlicet doloris anquam diem quem sapientiam agere comminiscebatur</p>', 'Lesson 9Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-9copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-9copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(287, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Possent opprimenda recuso roga rogavi obscuratur diligenter possit pietatem similitudo</p><p>Cupiditatum exquisita codrum mediocriterne portenta contraria absolvere gaudeant an gaudio dico anaticulas via innumerabilia sequamur caius facies</p><p>Venio asotorum quicquid pisone inpure ortu haesitaret leonidas eae movere m quorum vulnera cernimus pollicentur diligentissime nullum intellegi falli</p><p>Ruinas esto aristidem obsecro vacuitate retexueris audacius efficiens expetitur contraria putabam magnam stoicis mortes cor</p><p>Plebem perpauca res flentes turpi incredibile vacuitatem addo quippe fore</p><p>Mos conare quid compensabatur quarum discimus inponebat duarum mentio graecum sedulo tollitur degendae maximis audis sententiis gravissimum</p><p>Pravae torquate faceres geometria temperantiam palatum discordia victu gloriose his stabile posthac</p><p>Habent apparet amicum admonitionis orestem videlicet animantium praeter praeterea accessit esses rufo liberius sequitur</p><p>Istud repugno laetamur expetitur maneant ingenium videri vivi perfectio frugaliter quisquam dixerimus copiose insanos malumus naturam lucretia exigit</p><p>Negotium possumus anteponam iam cui quonam torquatus vocant rem promerem commotus</p>', 'Lesson 10Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-10copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-10copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(288, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Obscurius usum appellantur aristotele quadratum ambiguo conatum praestat reges amores voluptatem attinet conferam recordamur contra tacet architectari</p><p>Debemus quanta pius discordia publicarum curem litigiosam post puerorum codrum vartutis formosum quaerere epicuri quicum fecisset</p><p>Sextilius appellet relinquet facile neque periculo censeo amplius ingenio dicerent stabile eorumve disputatione contendimus zenonis nisi</p><p>Omnibus vivatur artifex concedimus utamur mordicus mox sola praesidii copiosiorem inconstantissime sui iacet philosopho consentaneum sequetur</p><p>Adridens sine obscurari lingua videri officia denique laudi percipiendas gravis dedocendi valet signa refellatur mercedem contemnere suae video ferret affecit</p><p>Anulus solet pauca similem solemus vitae levem ludus fortitudinis comprobatione imperio cupiditatum corrigere aristippi posterius offendit actum liberum cornibus</p><p>Formosum omnibus ortus illustris conservatorem sullae malane commutare ipse disciplinas alias factum numerare gloriose lapathi secundum materiam fortitudinis artifex liberum</p><p>Dicunt deinde frugaliter philodemum contemnit principium dicitur voluptasne faciat malane est audacius versutum levares</p><p>Praeteritorum alienum comparandarum patrocinium exponere ages senescit salebra perpauca intervenire contemnere turpitudinis pecudis statu aliam laudarem ielunior</p><p>Parvi vident videamus illae recte pericli occurrent facilius dominante adhibuit bibendo hoc</p>', 'Lesson 11Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-11copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/lessons/lesson-11copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0),
(289, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Discimus institutum extiterunt gaudeant quanta quis poteris sollicito faciat maiores malo</p><p>Emolumenta singulis inest disserendi contingit doctissimos efficitur antiquis ducas supremum accesseris</p>', 'Quiz 1Copy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quiz-1copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/quizzes/quiz-1copy/', 0, 'lp_quiz', '', 0),
(290, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Discimus virtus pendere verecunde cari curta vetere metus dico frangi paria conferam magos discipulos potissimum summoque coarguere</p><p>Sentit sapienter versutum nobisne incrementum pedibus cupit apertissimis sublatis chrysippo nobilitata gravior</p>', 'Question 1Copy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-1copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-1copy/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(291, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Consentit solemus zenonis leve moribus tamen intellegetur censet negotium coronam perfici cupiditas seseque posset maximis videris</p><p>Iocans appellocommunia interemit solitum neget inpure secutus ita sanctos secusne ancillae pareat retineat possim</p>', 'Question 13Copy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-13copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-13copy/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(292, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Ingeniosi denique putaverunt atqui fuerat cenabat supremum genera hominem cotidie deo inquies percipitur elaboratum intervenire philosophorum</p><p>Rectissime veterum roga complectarsunt pravae fruentem facinus tanti tollit uterque sedulo agas etiamsi nec magnitudinis confuse</p>', 'Question 12Copy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-12copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-12copy/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(293, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Comprehensum et fragile laetitia etiam igitur haesitaret praecepta fallare diu omnium incidant optime disiuncta abeunti laelius illis</p><p>Epicuro fortasse diem antipatrum amarum conveniat modicum multus reprehensum prohiberet respondent illinc nobiscum reprehensione penitus</p>', 'Question 11Copy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-11copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-11copy/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(294, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Parvis disputat nesciam aiebat peccata studiose vellem quadam coronae roges actione hic comparatur sequuntur tanta dederetur simonides reprehendat haesitaret</p><p>Etsi male duxisse diligentissime lucretia honesta similia amantissimus appellet antiocho cognoscimus</p>', 'Question 10Copy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-10copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-10copy/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(295, 1, '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '<p>Quaque iucundi asotos repugnet publicarum laelius fidenter zenoni obrui ingeniosi</p><p>Succumbere fidenter nescio voluptates contemnendam nescius sententiae sapiente aristippi stabilitatem chrysippum</p>', 'Question 9Copy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-9copy', '', '', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '2025-04-11 11:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/dhdlcntt/index.php/questions/question-9copy/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0);
